essed within %s business days.":"Your identity has been verified, and your payout will be processed within %s business days.","Up to %s files":"Up to %s files","Min. size: %s MP (%s×%s px)":"Min. size: %s MP (%s×%s px)","Clear images only: no blur, glare, or shadows. All details must be visible.":"Clear images only: no blur, glare, or shadows. All details must be visible.","Drag and drop your ID image(s) or \u003Cspan class=\"%s\"\u003Eclick here\u003C/span\u003E to upload":"Drag and drop your ID image(s) or \u003Cspan class=\"%s\"\u003Eclick here\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E to upload","Your payout request is under review. The payment will not be issued until you verify your identity. To do so, upload your ID or Passport photo to your account.":"Your payout request is under review. The payment will not be issued until you verify your identity. To do so, upload your ID or Passport photo to your account.","Your payout request is under review. The payment will not be issued until you verify your identity. To do so, upload a selfie holding your valid identity document to your account.":"Your payout request is under review. The payment will not be issued until you verify your identity. To do so, upload a selfie holding your valid identity document to your account.","Payout Action Required":"Payout Action Required","Confirm Identity":"Confirm Identity","Oops, the upload didn't go through. Please check your file and try again. If it still doesn't work, reach out to our \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\"\u003ECustomer Support team\u003C/a\u003E for help.":"Oops, the upload didn't go through. Please check your file and try again. If it still doesn't work, reach out to our \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\"\u003ECustomer Support team\u003C\u002Fa\u003E for help.","Your document has been uploaded successfully.":"Your document has been uploaded successfully.","We will contact you if we need any additional information.":"We will contact you if we need any additional information.","Discove