Folders","View Folder":"View Folder","%s selected":"%s selected","Drop files here":"Drop files here","Oops, you dont have any folders yet.":"Oops, you don't have any folders yet.","Just create a new one, then start collecting files you like.":"Just create a new one, then start collecting files you like.","License Files":"License Files","Day theme":"Day theme","Night theme":"Night theme","\u003Cspan class=\"%s\"\u003ECreate your Account\u003C/span\u003E to unlock all the features of Depositphotos":"\u003Cspan class=\"%s\"\u003ECreate your account\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E to unlock all the features of DepositPhotos","Please try to repeat this transaction using a different card or get in touch with your bank to resolve the payment issue.":"Please try to repeat this transaction using a different card or get in touch with your bank to resolve the payment issue.","Error: %s (%s).":"Error: %s (%s).","Please contact our \u003Ca href=\"%s\" class=\"%s\"\u003Esupport service\u003C/a\u003E or your card issuer.":"Please contact our \u003Ca href=\"%s\" class=\"%s\"\u003Esupport service\u003C\u002Fa\u003E or your card issuer.","Your transaction was declined by your bank. Please update your payment details required by your bank and submit the payment again.":"Your transaction was declined by your bank. Please update your payment details required by your bank and submit the payment again.","Invalid amount. Please use a different card, or resolve the issue with your bank and try again.":"Invalid amount. Please use a different card, or resolve the issue with your bank and try again.","The card has insufficient funds. Please use a different card or contact your card issuer.":"The card has insufficient funds. Please use a different card or contact your card issuer.","No checking account. Please try to repeat this transaction using a different card or contact your bank to resolve the payment issues.":"No checking account. Please try to repeat this transaction using a different card or contact your bank to resolve the payment issues.","No savings account. Please try to repeat this transaction using a different card or contact your bank to resolve the payment issues.":"No savings account. Please try to repeat this transaction using a different card or contact your bank to resolve the payment issues.","The card is expired. Please use a different card or contact your card issuer.":"The card is expired. Please use a different card or contact your card issuer.","It is possible that your online payment option is disabled. Please check with your card issuer to solve the problem.":"It is possible that your online payment option is disabled. Please check with your card issuer to solve the problem.","The transaction was declined because it would exceed your card's withdrawal limit. Contact your bank for details or consider using another payment method.":"The transaction was declined because it would exceed your card's withdrawal limit. Contact your bank for details or consider using another payment method.","Restricted card (card invalid in this region or country). Please try to repeat this transaction using a different card or contact your bank to resolve the payment issues.":"Restricted card (card invalid in this region or country). Please try to repeat this transaction using a different card or contact your bank to resolve the payment issues.","The bank reported a security issue with your card. Please use another payment method, or try again after resolving the issue with your bank.":"The bank reported a security issue with your card. Please use another payment method, or try again after resolving the issue with your bank.","Activity count limit for card exceeded. Please contact your card issuer.":"Activity count limit for card exceeded. Please contact your card issuer.","Allowable number of PIN tries exceeded. Please try to repeat this transaction using a different card or contact your bank to resolve the payment issues.":"Allowable number of PIN tries exceeded. Please try to repeat this transaction using a different card or contact your bank to resolve the payment issues.","Invalid / nonexistent account specified. Please try to repeat this transaction using a different card or contact your bank to resolve the payment issues.":"Invalid \u002F nonexistent account specified. Please try to repeat this transaction using a different card or contact your bank to resolve the payment issues.","The card issuer was unable to complete authentication due to internal problems. Please use a different card or try again later.":"The card issuer was unable to complete authentication due to internal problems. Please use a different card or try again later.","Transaction cannot be completed - violation of law. Please try to repeat this transaction using a different card or contact your bank to resolve the payment issues.":"Transaction cannot be completed - violation of law. Please try to repeat this transaction using a different card or contact your bank to resolve the payment issues.","Invalid Credit Card Number":"Invalid Credit Card Number","Invalid Security Code":"Invalid Security Code","Please check the Expiration Date":"Please check the Expiration Date.","Please check Street Address":"Please check Street Address","Invalid Zip/Postal Code":"Invalid ZIP\u002FPostal Code","Please check the cardholder's name":"Please check the cardholder's name","Invalid PIN":"Invalid PIN","Currency Type Not Accepted":"Currency Type Not Accepted","The card is blocked. Please use a different card or contact your card issuer.":"The card is blocked. Please use a different card or contact your card issuer.","Your IP blocked. Please contact our \u003Ca href=\"%s\" class=\"%s\"\u003Esupport service\u003C/a\u003E to resolve this problem.":"Your IP blocked. Please contact our \u003Ca href=\"%s\" class=\"%s\"\u003Esupport service\u003C\u002Fa\u003E to resolve this problem.","We were unable to process your payment at this time due to an additional security verification step. Please contact our \u003Ca href=\"%s\" class=\"%s\"\u003Esupport service\u003C/a\u003E for assistance.":"We were unable to process your payment at this time due to an additional security verification step. Please contact our \u003Ca href=\"%s\" class=\"%s\"\u003Esupport service\u003C\u002Fa\u003E for assistance.","Trial is unavailable":"Trial is unavailable","Looks like you signed up for a free trial before. You can purchase the plan to continue.":"Looks like you signed up for a free trial before. You can purchase the plan to continue.","Please enter your billing address and try again.":"Please enter your billing address and try again.","Transaction not exist or already processed.":"Transaction not exist or already processed.","Dear %s, we can process payments through %s with AMEX cards in USD only. Please choose another card or pick USD as the currency of payment.":"Dear %s, we can process payments through %s with AMEX cards in USD only. Please choose another card or pick USD as the currency of payment. ","We cannot process payments in current currency. Please choose another payment method or pick USD as the currency of payment.":"We cannot process payments in current currency. Please choose another payment method or pick USD as the currency of payment.","The payment currency must match the currency of your card. Please select a billing currency that is compatible with your card.":"The payment currency must match the currency of your card. Please select a billing currency that is compatible with your card.","This offer was created for a different account and cannot be purchased here.":"This offer was created for a different account and cannot be purchased here.","We are unable to process your payment at this time. Please contact our \u003Ca href=\"%s\" class=\"%s\"\u003Esupport service\u003C/a\u003E for assistance.":"We are unable to process your payment at this time. Please contact our \u003Ca href=\"%s\" class=\"%s\"\u003Esupport service\u003C\u002Fa\u003E for assistance.","Your rebill request is already being processed. To prevent duplicate charges, please wait a few moments for it to complete.":"Your rebill request is already being processed. To prevent duplicate charges, please wait a few moments for it to complete.","3d-secure authentication failed. Please contact your bank to find out the cause of the issue.":"3d-secure authentication failed. Please contact your bank to find out the cause of the issue.",Home:ba,API:"API",Team:"Team",Plans:"Plans","Seller Menu":"Seller's Menu",Authors:"Authors","Refer & Get up to $40 Cash":"Refer & Get up to $40 Cash","What are stock photos?":"What are stock photos?","\u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EStock photos\u003C/a\u003E are professional images created by photographers, designers, and other content contributors. Along with vectors and illustrations, they are distributed through content platforms like DepositPhotos. Stock photos offer a quick and cost-effective way to access high-quality images on almost any topic, suitable for a wide range of projects—from creative to commercial.":"\u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EStock photos\u003C\u002Fa\u003E are professional images created by photographers, designers, and other content contributors. Along with vectors and illustrations, they are distributed through content platforms like DepositPhotos. Stock photos offer a quick and cost-effective way to access high-quality images on almost any topic, suitable for a wide range of projects—from creative to commercial.","What is royalty-free stock photography?":"What is royalty-free stock photography?","Royalty-free stock photography means that images are sold under a license that allows you to pay for an image once and use it for an unlimited period, as specified in the terms of the agreement. This type of license means you don’t have to pay royalties for each additional use. With a royalty-free license, images are available on a non-exclusive basis and can be purchased by anyone.":"Royalty-free stock photography means that images are sold under a license that allows you to pay for an image once and use it for an unlimited period, as specified in the terms of the agreement. This type of license means you don’t have to pay royalties for each additional use. With a royalty-free license, images are available on a non-exclusive basis and can be purchased by anyone.","What is the difference between “royalty-free” and “free to use” images?":"What is the difference between “royalty-free” and “free to use” images?","\u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003E“Royalty-free”\u003C/a\u003E does not mean that images are free to use. Instead, it refers to a \u003Cstrong\u003Estock photo licensing\u003C/strong\u003E model that grants you \u003Cstrong\u003Eimage rights\u003C/strong\u003E after a one-time payment, providing indefinite access without additional royalties for each application.":"\u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003E“Royalty-free”\u003C\u002Fa\u003E does not mean that images are free to use. Instead, it refers to a \u003Cstrong\u003Estock photo licensing\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E model that grants you \u003Cstrong\u003Eimage rights\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E after a one-time payment, providing indefinite access without additional royalties for each application.","Although DepositPhotos primarily distributes royalty-free files, we also offer a large collection of \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Efree images\u003C/a\u003E that can be downloaded at no cost for personal or business purposes. The only requirement when using free visuals is proper attribution of the source.":"Although DepositPhotos primarily distributes royalty-free files, we also offer a large collection of \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Efree images\u003C\u002Fa\u003E that can be downloaded at no cost for personal or business purposes. The only requirement when using free visuals is proper attribution of the source.","Can you make money selling stock photography?":"Can you make money selling stock photography?","Yes. If you are a professional photographer or an enthusiast who produces images with commercial appeal, you can upload and sell your photos on content platforms, including \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EDepositPhotos\u003C/a\u003E.":"Yes. If you are a professional photographer or an enthusiast who produces images with commercial appeal, you can upload and sell your photos on content platforms, including \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EDepositPhotos\u003C\u002Fa\u003E.","To \u003Cstrong\u003Emake money\u003C/strong\u003E from \u003Cstrong\u003Estock photos\u003C/strong\u003E on DepositPhotos, you need to \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Ebecome a contributor\u003C/a\u003E:":"To \u003Cstrong\u003Emake money\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E from \u003Cstrong\u003Estock photos\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E on DepositPhotos, you need to \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Ebecome a contributor\u003C\u002Fa\u003E:","\u003Cstrong\u003EStep 1.\u003C/strong\u003E Register as a contributor on our website.":"\u003Cstrong\u003EStep 1.\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E Register as a contributor on our website.","\u003Cstrong\u003EStep 2.\u003C/strong\u003E Upload your five best files for examination.":"\u003Cstrong\u003EStep 2.\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E Upload your five best files for examination.","\u003Cstrong\u003EStep 3.\u003C/strong\u003E After passing the examination, begin building your portfolio with photos.":"\u003Cstrong\u003EStep 3.\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E After passing the examination, begin building your portfolio with photos.","Important note: To \u003Cstrong\u003Esell photos on DepositPhotos\u003C/strong\u003E, you must be at least 18 years old.":"Important note: To \u003Cstrong\u003Esell photos on DepositPhotos\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E, you must be at least 18 years old.","How much money can photographers and creators realistically make selling stock photography on DepositPhotos?":"How much money can photographers and creators realistically make selling stock photography on DepositPhotos?","\u003Cstrong\u003EStock photography contributor earnings\u003C/strong\u003E depend on \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Eyour level\u003C/a\u003E and start from $0.25 per download. The \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Emore files you sell\u003C/a\u003E, the higher your contributor level and overall income. Commissions are also influenced by the type of license under which the photo is sold and the resolution at which it is purchased.":"\u003Cstrong\u003EStock photography contributor earnings\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E depend on \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Eyour level\u003C\u002Fa\u003E and start from $0.25 per download. The \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Emore files you sell\u003C\u002Fa\u003E, the higher your contributor level and overall income. Commissions are also influenced by the type of license under which the photo is sold and the resolution at which it is purchased. ","How much do stock pictures cost?":"How much do stock pictures cost?","The cost of photos varies depending on the content platform. Prices also differ based on the type of plan and license you select. DepositPhotos offers \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Eaffordable image plans\u003C/a\u003E for both individuals and businesses, with prices starting at just $0.19 per download.":"The cost of photos varies depending on the content platform. Prices also differ based on the type of plan and license you select. DepositPhotos offers \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Eaffordable image plans\u003C\u002Fa\u003E for both individuals and businesses, with prices starting at just $0.19 per download.","Where can I find free stock photos on DepositPhotos?":"Where can I find free stock photos on DepositPhotos?","You can find our \u003Cstrong\u003Efree stock photography collection\u003C/strong\u003E in the Images section of the website header (select \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EFree pictures\u003C/a\u003E from the dropdown menu) or in the website footer. You can also apply the Free filter in the search bar to display only \u003Cstrong\u003Efree DepositPhotos images\u003C/strong\u003E.":"You can find our \u003Cstrong\u003Efree stock photography collection\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E in the Images section of the website header (select \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EFree pictures\u003C\u002Fa\u003E from the dropdown menu) or in the website footer. You can also apply the Free filter in the search bar to display only \u003Cstrong\u003Efree DepositPhotos images\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E.","What license types are available (Standard vs Extended), and what do they allow businesses to do?":"What license types are available (Standard vs Extended), and what do they allow businesses to do?","DepositPhotos offers two \u003Cstrong\u003Estock photo license types\u003C/strong\u003E: \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EStandard and Extended\u003C/a\u003E. Both allow businesses to use purchased images across various digital and print materials, including social media, websites, apps, packaging, brochures, and more.":"DepositPhotos offers two \u003Cstrong\u003Estock photo license types\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E: \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EStandard and Extended\u003C\u002Fa\u003E. Both allow businesses to use purchased images across various digital and print materials, including social media, websites, apps, packaging, brochures, and more.","When comparing the \u003Cstrong\u003EStandard vs Extended license\u003C/strong\u003E, the difference comes down to usage rights:":"When comparing the \u003Cstrong\u003EStandard vs Extended license\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E, the difference comes down to usage rights:","A \u003Cstrong\u003EStandard License\u003C/strong\u003E covers the most common personal and commercial purposes. It allows up to 500,000 copies but excludes items for resale where stock images add significant value.":"A \u003Cstrong\u003EStandard License\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E covers the most common personal and commercial purposes. It allows up to 500,000 copies but excludes items for resale where stock images add significant value.","An \u003Cstrong\u003EExtended License\u003C/strong\u003E includes all Standard rights, removes print limits, and additionally allows the creation of items for resale or free distribution.":"An \u003Cstrong\u003EExtended License\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E includes all Standard rights, removes print limits, and additionally allows the creation of items for resale or free distribution.","How can companies purchase Extended licenses for resale products such as t-shirts or posters?":"How can companies purchase Extended licenses for resale products such as t-shirts or posters?","If your company plans to use stock images for products intended for resale, you’ll need to \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Epurchase Packs\u003C/a\u003E with an Extended License. Each Pack provides a set number of image downloads (5, 10, 25, or 50), valid for one year from the date of purchase. You can download the files at any time within a year as needed.":"If your company plans to use stock images for products intended for resale, you’ll need to \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Epurchase Packs\u003C\u002Fa\u003E with an Extended License. Each Pack provides a set number of image downloads (5, 10, 25, or 50), valid for one year from the date of purchase. You can download the files at any time within a year as needed.","What are the most common license restrictions I should be aware of before using images commercially?":"What are the most common license restrictions I should be aware of before using images commercially?","The \u003Cstrong\u003Ecommercial use\u003C/strong\u003E of stock images requires the \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Eright license\u003C/a\u003E and an understanding of \u003Cstrong\u003Estock photo license restrictions\u003C/strong\u003E. The Standard License covers the most common uses but limits print runs to 500,000 copies and excludes products for resale or free distribution where the image adds significant value. In those cases, you’ll need an Extended License.":"The \u003Cstrong\u003Ecommercial use\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E of stock images requires the \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Eright license\u003C\u002Fa\u003E and an understanding of \u003Cstrong\u003Estock photo license restrictions\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E. The Standard License covers the most common uses but limits print runs to 500,000 copies and excludes products for resale or free distribution where the image adds significant value. In those cases, you’ll need an Extended License.","Should I choose a subscription plan or an image pack for my business?":"Should I choose a subscription plan or an image pack for my business?","Choosing the \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Ebest plan for your business\u003C/a\u003E depends on how often you need stock images:":"Choosing the \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Ebest plan for your business\u003C\u002Fa\u003E depends on how often you need stock images:","A \u003Cstrong\u003Estock photo subscription\u003C/strong\u003E is the ideal option if your company requires a steady stream of visuals for ongoing content creation.":"A \u003Cstrong\u003Estock photo subscription\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E is the ideal option if your company requires a steady stream of visuals for ongoing content creation.","\u003Cstrong\u003EImage packs\u003C/strong\u003E are the better choice if you only need visuals occasionally for specific campaigns or projects.":"\u003Cstrong\u003EImage packs\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E are the better choice if you only need visuals occasionally for specific campaigns or projects.","How do I ensure my brand stands out with unique stock content?":"How do I ensure my brand stands out with unique stock content?","To make your brand stand out, \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Echoose images\u003C/a\u003E that reflect your brand’s voice and visual identity. If you want to discover \u003Cstrong\u003Eniche stock photos\u003C/strong\u003E, try these tips:":"To make your brand stand out, \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Echoose images\u003C\u002Fa\u003E that reflect your brand’s voice and visual identity. If you want to discover \u003Cstrong\u003Eniche stock photos\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E, try these tips:","Use the “Fresh” option in \u003Cstrong\u003Eadvanced search filters\u003C/strong\u003E to find trending files that haven’t been widely used.":"Use the “Fresh” option in \u003Cstrong\u003Eadvanced search filters\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E to find trending files that haven’t been widely used.","Browse our thematic collections and curated DepositPhotos blog collections for hand-picked visuals.":"Browse our thematic collections and curated DepositPhotos blog collections for hand-picked visuals.","Follow authors whose style aligns with your brand and search for images directly within their portfolios.":"Follow authors whose style aligns with your brand and search for images directly within their portfolios.","Does DepositPhotos offer AI-generated content, and how is it licensed?":"Does DepositPhotos offer AI-generated content, and how is it licensed?","DepositPhotos does not accept AI-generated content from contributors. However, users can create their own unique visuals with our built-in \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EAI Image Generator\u003C/a\u003E. Simply enter a text prompt and get four \u003Cstrong\u003EAI-generated stock photos\u003C/strong\u003E in seconds.":"DepositPhotos does not accept AI-generated content from contributors. However, users can create their own unique visuals with our built-in \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EAI Image Generator\u003C\u002Fa\u003E. Simply enter a text prompt and get four \u003Cstrong\u003EAI-generated stock photos\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E in seconds.","Every DepositPhotos plan includes unlimited generations, with downloads counted the same way as files from the main library. All AI-generated images are provided under the Standard License, ensuring clear \u003Cstrong\u003EAI licensing\u003C/strong\u003E terms for safe commercial use.":"Every DepositPhotos plan includes unlimited generations, with downloads counted the same way as files from the main library. All AI-generated images are provided under the Standard License, ensuring clear \u003Cstrong\u003EAI licensing\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E terms for safe commercial use.","How can AI tools like the Background Remover, Image Generator, and Upscaler save time in my creative workflow?":"How can AI tools like the Background Remover, Image Generator, and Upscaler save time in my creative workflow?","Manually erasing backgrounds, enlarging images, or creating visuals from scratch can take hours. Tools like the \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EBackground Remover\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/a\u003E, \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EAI Image Generator\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/a\u003E, or \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EUpscaler\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/a\u003E reduce this to minutes, sometimes even seconds, freeing up time from routine work and helping you optimize your \u003Cstrong\u003Ecreative workflow\u003C/strong\u003E.":"Manually erasing backgrounds, enlarging images, or creating visuals from scratch can take hours. Tools like the \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EBackground Remover\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E\u003C\u002Fa\u003E, \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EAI Image Generator\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E\u003C\u002Fa\u003E, or \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EUpscaler\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E\u003C\u002Fa\u003E reduce this to minutes, sometimes even seconds, freeing up time from routine work and helping you optimize your \u003Cstrong\u003Ecreative workflow\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E.","Stock photos are images that are created by photographers, designers, and other content contributors. These images usually feature different file types that include photos, vectors, and illustrations. Stock photography websites such as Depositphotos are a source of income for contributors who get royalty payments from Depositphotos when their works are downloaded. When you buy stock photos from Depositphotos, you only pay for them once and can use them for different purposes, including commercial or editorial ones. Stock photos can help you boost your creative projects in an affordable way.":"Stock photos are images that are created by photographers, designers, and other content contributors. These images usually feature different file types that include photos, vectors, and illustrations. Stock photography websites such as Depositphotos are a source of income for contributors who get royalty payments from Depositphotos when their works are downloaded. When you buy stock photos from Depositphotos, you only pay for them once and can use them for different purposes, including commercial or editorial ones. Stock photos can help you boost your creative projects in an affordable way.","Royalty-free stock photography means that images are sold under a type of license that allows you to pay for an image once and use it forever according to the agreement. This type of license means you don’t have to pay royalties for each consequent use. With a royalty-free license, images can be purchased by anyone on a non-exclusive basis.":"Royalty-free stock photography means that images are sold under a type of license that allows you to pay for an image once and use it forever according to the agreement. This type of license means you don’t have to pay royalties for each consequent use. With a royalty-free license, images can be purchased by anyone on a non-exclusive basis.","How much do stock photos cost?":"How much do stock photos cost?","The cost of stock photos varies depending on the stock photography agency and the website you use. Prices range anywhere from $0.22 to $89 per image on Depositphotos. The price will be different according to the type of plan and license you choose for your needs.":"The cost of stock photos varies depending on the stock photography agency and the website you use. Prices range anywhere from $0.22 to $89 per image on Depositphotos. The price will be different according to the type of plan and license you choose for your needs.","Where can you find free stock photos?":"Where can you find free stock photos?","Some stock photography websites have a separate section for free stock photos. On Depositphotos, you can find a collection of free files in the footer section of the website.":"Some stock photography websites have a separate section for free stock photos. On Depositphotos, you can find a collection of free files in the footer section of the website.","Yes. If you are a professional photographer or even an enthusiast who produces images that have commercial appeal, you can upload your photos to stock photography websites.":"Yes. If you are a professional photographer or even an enthusiast who produces images that have commercial appeal, you can upload your photos to stock photography websites.","What is a vector?":"What is a vector?","\u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EVectors\u003C/a\u003E are images created with computer software. These graphics are made of shapes and lines based on mathematical equations. What makes such images unique is that they can be scaled to any size without loss of quality.":"\u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EVectors\u003C\u002Fa\u003E are images created with computer software. These graphics are made of shapes and lines based on mathematical equations. What makes such images unique is that they can be scaled to any size without loss of quality.","Where can I sell stock vectors?":"Where can I sell stock vectors?","Graphic designers and other digital artists can create vector images to upload and sell on stock photography platforms such as DepositPhotos. To do this, they must \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Ebecome contributors\u003C/a\u003E by signing up to a stock platform and submitting their images for review.":"Graphic designers and other digital artists can create vector images to upload and sell on stock photography platforms such as DepositPhotos. To do this, they must \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Ebecome contributors\u003C\u002Fa\u003E by signing up to a stock platform and submitting their images for review.","How to sell stock vectors on DepositPhotos?":"How to sell stock vectors on DepositPhotos?","To \u003Cstrong\u003Emake money with vector graphics\u003C/strong\u003E on DepositPhotos, you’ll need to \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Ebecome a contributor\u003C/a\u003E:":"To \u003Cstrong\u003Emake money with vector graphics\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E on DepositPhotos, you’ll need to \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Ebecome a contributor\u003C\u002Fa\u003E:","\u003Cstrong\u003EStep 2.\u003C/strong\u003E Upload your five best vector files for examination.":"\u003Cstrong\u003EStep 2.\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E Upload your five best vector files for examination.","\u003Cstrong\u003EStep 3.\u003C/strong\u003E Once you pass the examination, start building your portfolio with vectors.":"\u003Cstrong\u003EStep 3.\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E Once you pass the examination, start building your portfolio with vectors.","Important: To become a \u003Cstrong\u003EDepositPhotos vector contributor\u003C/strong\u003E, you must be at least 18 years old.":"Important: To become a \u003Cstrong\u003EDepositPhotos vector contributor\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E, you must be at least 18 years old.","Are stock vector images available for commercial use?":"Are stock vector images available for commercial use?","Vector images are available on stock photography platforms and sold under a \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EStandard License\u003C/a\u003E or \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EExtended License\u003C/a\u003E, with the latter allowing you to use these graphics for commercial purposes (except being officially registered as a trademark). Restrictions are based on how and where you plan to use the royalty-free image of your choice.":"Vector images are available on stock photography platforms and sold under a \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EStandard License\u003C\u002Fa\u003E or \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EExtended License\u003C\u002Fa\u003E, with the latter allowing you to use these graphics for commercial purposes (except being officially registered as a trademark). Restrictions are based on how and where you plan to use the royalty-free image of your choice.","What license is required for printing on merchandise (T-shirts, mugs)?":"What license is required for printing on merchandise (T-shirts, mugs)?","Both our license models—\u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EStandard and Extended\u003C/a\u003E—permit the \u003Cstrong\u003Ecommercial use of stock vectors\u003C/strong\u003E, including printing on merchandise. If you plan to use a vector image to create items such as T-shirts, mugs, or other products for resale or free distribution, where the vector is a key design element, choose the Extended license.":"Both our license models—\u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EStandard and Extended\u003C\u002Fa\u003E—permit the \u003Cstrong\u003Ecommercial use of stock vectors\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E, including printing on merchandise. If you plan to use a vector image to create items such as T-shirts, mugs, or other products for resale or free distribution, where the vector is a key design element, choose the Extended license.","When do I need an Extended License for a stock vector instead of a Standard License?":"When do I need an Extended License for a stock vector instead of a Standard License?","You should choose an \u003Cstrong\u003EExtended License\u003C/strong\u003E over a \u003Cstrong\u003EStandard License\u003C/strong\u003E if you plan to:":"You should choose an \u003Cstrong\u003EExtended License\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E over a \u003Cstrong\u003EStandard License\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E if you plan to:","Use a stock vector to create items for \u003Cstrong\u003Eresale\u003C/strong\u003E or free distribution, where the file plays a major role in the final product (e.g., web templates, calendars, T-shirts, etc.).":"Use a stock vector to create items for \u003Cstrong\u003Eresale\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E or free distribution, where the file plays a major role in the final product (e.g., web templates, calendars, T-shirts, etc.).","Create books, magazines, newspapers, and marketing materials with over 500,000 copies.":"Create books, magazines, newspapers, and marketing materials with over 500,000 copies.","What formats of stock vectors are available?":"What formats of stock vectors are available?","Common formats for stock vectors include SVG, EPS, PDF, or AI files. Raster image formats include JPEG, PNG, APNG, GIF, and MPEG4. Note that not all file formats allow scaling.":"Common formats for stock vectors include SVG, EPS, PDF, or AI files. Raster image formats include JPEG, PNG, APNG, GIF, and MPEG4. Note that not all file formats allow scaling.","Which vector file format (AI, EPS, SVG) should I choose for my project?":"Which vector file format (AI, EPS, SVG) should I choose for my project?","Depending on your specific project, consider the following \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Estock vector\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/a\u003E formats:":"Depending on your specific project, consider the following \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Estock vector\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E\u003C\u002Fa\u003E formats:","\u003Cstrong\u003EEPS\u003C/strong\u003E files—a universal \u003Cstrong\u003Eformat\u003C/strong\u003E ideal for high-quality printing and compatibility with most design software.":"\u003Cstrong\u003EEPS\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E files—a universal \u003Cstrong\u003Eformat\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E ideal for high-quality printing and compatibility with most design software.","\u003Cstrong\u003EAI files\u003C/strong\u003E—the native Adobe Illustrator format, perfect for branding, illustrations, and packaging design.":"\u003Cstrong\u003EAI files\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E—the native Adobe Illustrator format, perfect for branding, illustrations, and packaging design.","\u003Cstrong\u003ESVG files\u003C/strong\u003E—best for digital use, especially responsive web design, where scalability and fast loading are essential.":"\u003Cstrong\u003ESVG files\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E—best for digital use, especially responsive web design, where scalability and fast loading are essential.","What are the technical advantages of vector scalability for businesses?":"What are the technical advantages of vector scalability for businesses?","\u003Cstrong\u003EVector scalability\u003C/strong\u003E allows for resizing images infinitely without losing quality. This makes vectors ideal for businesses that need consistent visuals across multiple formats, from small \u003Cstrong\u003Ewebsite icons\u003C/strong\u003E to large \u003Cstrong\u003Ebillboards\u003C/strong\u003E.":"\u003Cstrong\u003EVector scalability\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E allows for resizing images infinitely without losing quality. This makes vectors ideal for businesses that need consistent visuals across multiple formats, from small \u003Cstrong\u003Ewebsite icons\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E to large \u003Cstrong\u003Ebillboards\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E.","Can I legally use a stock vector in my company logo or trademarked design?":"Can I legally use a stock vector in my company logo or trademarked design?","No, you cannot use \u003Cstrong\u003Evectors for logos\u003C/strong\u003E or trademarked designs. The copyright of any image from a stock content website does not transfer to you under a royalty-free license. Additionally, royalty-free images are available to all users, which means they cannot provide the uniqueness required for a logo or a \u003Cstrong\u003Estock vector brand design\u003C/strong\u003E. Instead, you can create a custom design using the \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EFree Logomaker\u003C/a\u003E.":"No, you cannot use \u003Cstrong\u003Evectors for logos\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E or trademarked designs. The copyright of any image from a stock content website does not transfer to you under a royalty-free license. Additionally, royalty-free images are available to all users, which means they cannot provide the uniqueness required for a logo or a \u003Cstrong\u003Estock vector brand design\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E. Instead, you can create a custom design using the \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EFree Logomaker\u003C\u002Fa\u003E.","How can I buy a stock vector?":"How can I buy a stock vector?","To get vector images, you must \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Esign up\u003C/a\u003E for an account on a stock content platform if you haven’t already and purchase a suitable subscription or plan for downloading files. You can also buy a single image. To do so, choose to pay using \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EImage Packs\u003C/a\u003E.":"To get vector images, you must \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Esign up\u003C\u002Fa\u003E for an account on a stock content platform if you haven’t already and purchase a suitable subscription or plan for downloading files. You can also buy a single image. To do so, choose to pay using \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EImage Packs\u003C\u002Fa\u003E.","How can I edit a vector file?":"How can I edit a vector file?","A royalty-free vector image comes as a ZIP archive containing two formats (JPEG and EPS/AI). These files are scalable to any size. To modify AI or EPS files, you need a specific editing software like Adobe Illustrator. To process JPEG files, you can use tools like \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EFree Background Remover\u003C/a\u003E and \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EImage Upscaler\u003C/a\u003E.":"A royalty-free vector image comes as a ZIP archive containing two formats (JPEG and EPS\u002FAI). These files are scalable to any size. To modify AI or EPS files, you need a specific editing software like Adobe Illustrator. To process JPEG files, you can use tools like \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EFree Background Remover\u003C\u002Fa\u003E and \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EImage Upscaler\u003C\u002Fa\u003E.","What if I didn’t find the image I need?":"What if I didn’t find the image I need?","If you don’t find the royalty-free image you’re looking for, you can create a unique visual with \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EAI Image Generator\u003C/a\u003E. It works based on text prompts. Simply describe the image you need and get a licensed file suitable for any project in no time.":"If you don’t find the royalty-free image you’re looking for, you can create a unique visual with \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EAI Image Generator\u003C\u002Fa\u003E. It works based on text prompts. Simply describe the image you need and get a licensed file suitable for any project in no time.","How can I find the perfect vector for a specific business project?":"How can I find the perfect vector for a specific business project?","To \u003Cstrong\u003Efind the perfect vector\u003C/strong\u003E for any project, use \u003Cstrong\u003Eadvanced search filters\u003C/strong\u003E together with your keyword or request. These filters help you narrow down results by specifying image orientation, the presence of people, point of view, color, season, and more. If your \u003Cstrong\u003Ecreative brief\u003C/strong\u003E includes an image reference, you can also use \u003Cstrong\u003Ereverse image search\u003C/strong\u003E to find a similar vector in the DepositPhotos library quickly.":"To \u003Cstrong\u003Efind the perfect vector\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E for any project, use \u003Cstrong\u003Eadvanced search filters\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E together with your keyword or request. These filters help you narrow down results by specifying image orientation, the presence of people, point of view, color, season, and more. If your \u003Cstrong\u003Ecreative brief\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E includes an image reference, you can also use \u003Cstrong\u003Ereverse image search\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E to find a similar vector in the DepositPhotos library quickly.","What are stock vectors?":"What are stock vectors?","Stock vectors are a type of vector graphics, which is art created with the help of computer software. The elements are made up of shapes and lines based on a mathematical formula. What makes this type of graphic unique is that it can be scaled to any size without quality loss.":"Stock vectors are a type of vector graphics, which is art created with the help of computer software. The elements are made up of shapes and lines based on a mathematical formula. What makes this type of graphic unique is that it can be scaled to any size without quality loss.","Graphic designers and other digital artists can create their own vector graphics to upload and sell them on stock photography platforms.":"Graphic designers and other digital artists can create their own vector graphics to upload and sell them on stock photography platforms.","Are stock vectors available for commercial use?":"Are stock vectors available for commercial use?","Vector graphics available on stock photography platforms are also sold under a Standard or Extended royalty-free license, with the latter allowing you to use the vectors for commercial purposes (except being officially registered as a trademark). Restrictions are based on how and where you plan to use the image.":"Vector graphics available on stock photography platforms are also sold under a Standard or Extended royalty-free license, with the latter allowing you to use the vectors for commercial purposes (except being officially registered as a trademark). Restrictions are based on how and where you plan to use the image.","Common formats for vector graphics include SVG, EPS, PDF, or AI files. Raster graphic formats can include JPEG, PNG, APNG, GIF, and MPEG4. Mind that not all the available file formats allow for scaling.":"Common formats for vector graphics include SVG, EPS, PDF, or AI files. Raster graphic formats can include JPEG, PNG, APNG, GIF, and MPEG4. Mind that not all the available file formats allow for scaling.","Can I use stock vectors as a logo?":"Can I use stock vectors as a logo?","No. You cannot use stock vectors in logos as the copyright of an image from a stock photography website does not belong to you under the royalty-free license. Also, stock vectors are available to everyone which would not make your logo unique.":"No. You cannot use stock vectors in logos as the copyright of an image from a stock photography website does not belong to you under the royalty-free license. Also, stock vectors are available to everyone which would not make your logo unique.","What is editorial photography?":"What Is Editorial Photography?","Editorial photos are \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Ephotos\u003C/a\u003E for \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Eeditorial purposes\u003C/a\u003E sold under an editorial license. They showcase people, events, landmarks, or other symbols and cannot be used for commercial purposes.":"Editorial photos are \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Ephotos\u003C\u002Fa\u003E for \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Eeditorial purposes\u003C\u002Fa\u003E sold under an editorial license. They showcase people, events, landmarks, or other symbols and cannot be used for commercial purposes.","What is the difference between editorial photography and commercial photography?":"What is the difference between editorial photography and commercial photography?","Editorial photography is used to illustrate stories and newsworthy events for educational/informative purposes only. \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003ECommercial photography\u003C/a\u003E is used to promote a range of products or services, and requires proper model/property release forms.":"Editorial photography is used to illustrate stories and newsworthy events for educational\u002Finformative purposes only. \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003ECommercial photography\u003C\u002Fa\u003E is used to promote a range of products or services, and requires proper model\u002Fproperty release forms.","Where can you use editorial photography?":"Where can you use editorial photography?","You can use \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Eeditorial photography\u003C/a\u003E to help illustrate an event or tell a story — e.g., in newspaper articles, magazine articles, blog posts, and other content needing informative visuals. Cannot be used to promote or sell products/services.":"You can use \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Eeditorial photography\u003C\u002Fa\u003E to help illustrate an event or tell a story — e.g., in newspaper articles, magazine articles, blog posts, and other content needing informative visuals. Cannot be used to promote or sell products\u002Fservices.","Where can you sell editorial photography?":"Where can you sell editorial photography?","You can \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Esell editorial photos\u003C/a\u003E on stock content platforms such as DepositPhotos. When uploading, ensure to specify that your files are intended for editorial use, so they are correctly categorized and licensed.":"You can \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Esell editorial photos\u003C\u002Fa\u003E on stock content platforms such as DepositPhotos. When uploading, ensure to specify that your files are intended for editorial use, so they are correctly categorized and licensed.","How can I sell my editorial photos on DepositPhotos?":"How can I sell my editorial photos on DepositPhotos?","To \u003Cstrong\u003Esell editorial photos\u003C/strong\u003E on our platform, you’ll need to become a DepositPhotos contributor:":"To \u003Cstrong\u003Esell editorial photos\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E on our platform, you’ll need to become a DepositPhotos contributor:","\u003Cstrong\u003EStep 2.\u003C/strong\u003E Upload your five best photos for examination.":"\u003Cstrong\u003EStep 2.\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E Upload your five best photos for examination.","\u003Cstrong\u003EStep 3.\u003C/strong\u003E Once you pass the examination, start building your portfolio with editorial photos.":"\u003Cstrong\u003EStep 3.\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E Once you pass the examination, start building your portfolio with editorial photos.","For more details, check out the \u003Cstrong\u003EDepositPhotos\u003C/strong\u003E \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Econtributor guide\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/a\u003E.":"For more details, check out the \u003Cstrong\u003EDepositPhotos\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Econtributor guide\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E\u003C\u002Fa\u003E.","What are the restrictions and legal risks of using editorial images?":"What are the restrictions and legal risks of using editorial images?","\u003Cstrong\u003EEditorial image restrictions\u003C/strong\u003E apply to commercial use. Because these files may include people without model releases, famous trademarks, or other protected elements, using them commercially can lead to \u003Cstrong\u003Elegal risks\u003C/strong\u003E. \u003Cstrong\u003EEditorial photos\u003C/strong\u003E should only be used in news, educational, or other non-commercial projects.":"\u003Cstrong\u003EEditorial image restrictions\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E apply to commercial use. Because these files may include people without model releases, famous trademarks, or other protected elements, using them commercially can lead to \u003Cstrong\u003Elegal risks\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E. \u003Cstrong\u003EEditorial photos\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E should only be used in news, educational, or other non-commercial projects.","What business scenarios are editorial images best suited for?":"What business scenarios are editorial images best suited for?","Editorial images can be used only in non-commercial business scenarios intended to inform or educate rather than promote.":"Editorial images can be used only in non-commercial business scenarios intended to inform or educate rather than promote.","\u003Cstrong\u003EBest editorial applications\u003C/strong\u003E include:":"\u003Cstrong\u003EBest editorial applications\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E include:","Blog posts covering current events or trends":"Blog posts covering current events or trends","Educational online courses, presentations, or reports":"Educational online courses, presentations, or reports","Corporate communication without advertising":"Corporate communication without advertising","What kind of subjects and content are available?":"What kind of subjects and content are available?","\u003Cstrong\u003EEditorial photography subjects\u003C/strong\u003E include real-world events, people, or places captured to illustrate current or newsworthy topics. In the DepositPhotos library, you’ll find a wide range of \u003Cstrong\u003Eavailable editorial content\u003C/strong\u003E covering everything from military conflicts and politics to sports, entertainment, and cultural events.":"\u003Cstrong\u003EEditorial photography subjects\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E include real-world events, people, or places captured to illustrate current or newsworthy topics. In the DepositPhotos library, you’ll find a wide range of \u003Cstrong\u003Eavailable editorial content\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E covering everything from military conflicts and politics to sports, entertainment, and cultural events.","Where does the editorial content come from, and who is it for?":"Where does the editorial content come from, and who is it for?","\u003Cstrong\u003EEditorial image providers\u003C/strong\u003E are professional photographers, photojournalists, and verified contributors who capture events, people, and places worldwide.":"\u003Cstrong\u003EEditorial image providers\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E are professional photographers, photojournalists, and verified contributors who capture events, people, and places worldwide.","The \u003Cstrong\u003Eeditorial content audience\u003C/strong\u003E includes media outlets, publishers, journalists, educators, and organizations that use such files to inform, illustrate, or educate.":"The \u003Cstrong\u003Eeditorial content audience\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E includes media outlets, publishers, journalists, educators, and organizations that use such files to inform, illustrate, or educate.","What are stock videos?":"What are stock videos?","Stock videos, or stock footage, are short video clips that are available for purchase on stock photography websites.":"Stock videos, or stock footage, are short video clips that are available for purchase on stock photography websites.","Where can you use stock videos?":"Where can you use stock videos?","Stock videos can be used as parts of a video to help you save costs on production. Most stock videos are used as part of a larger production for this purpose. You can find stock videos on a wide range of concepts and themes to fit your project.":"Stock videos can be used as parts of a video to help you save costs on production. Most stock videos are used as part of a larger production for this purpose. You can find stock videos on a wide range of concepts and themes to fit your project.","Are stock videos expensive?":"Are stock videos expensive?","On Depositphotos, prices can vary between $12.76 to $169 per stock video, depending on the resolution of the video. Stock footage is available in the following resolutions: 240p, 480p, 720p, 1080p, and 4K.":"On Depositphotos, prices can vary between $12.76 to $169 per stock video, depending on the resolution of the video. Stock footage is available in the following resolutions: 240p, 480p, 720p, 1080p, and 4K.","Can you get free stock videos?":"Can you get free stock videos?","Some websites offer free stock videos, however, it is likely that they do not come with the proper license type to allow you to use the footage for commercial purposes.":"Some websites offer free stock videos, however, it is likely that they do not come with the proper license type to allow you to use the footage for commercial purposes.","Can you edit stock videos?":"Can you edit stock videos?","You can add text and other effects to stock videos but check the license type to make sure you can do extensive modification of the original file or use it for commercial purposes.":"You can add text and other effects to stock videos but check the license type to make sure you can do extensive modification of the original file or use it for commercial purposes.","What are stock illustrations?":"What are stock illustrations?","Stock illustrations are pieces of art created by traditional means or with the help of computer software. This can include paintings, clip art, drawings, sketches, and other forms of traditional and digital art.":"Stock illustrations are pieces of art created by traditional means or with the help of computer software. This can include paintings, clip art, drawings, sketches, and other forms of traditional and digital art.","What types of stock illustrations can you buy?":"What types of stock illustrations can you buy?","Often, you will find many different categories of illustrations available on stock photography platforms such as classic art, cartoons, pop art, computer graphics, watercolor, acrylic works.":"Often, you will find many different categories of illustrations available on stock photography platforms such as classic art, cartoons, pop art, computer graphics, watercolor, acrylic works.","What is the difference between stock illustrations and vectors?":"What is the difference between stock illustrations and vectors?","Stock illustrations are usually uploaded in a JPEG format and scaling the image beyond its set size will make it blurry or distorted. Vector graphics are made of vectors and can therefore be scaled to any size.":"Stock illustrations are usually uploaded in a JPEG format and scaling the image beyond its set size will make it blurry or distorted. Vector graphics are made of vectors and can therefore be scaled to any size.","Where can you get free stock illustrations?":"Where can you get free stock illustrations?","Some stock photography websites such as Depositphotos have a separate section for stock illustrations in the header section of the website.":"Some stock photography websites such as Depositphotos have a separate section for stock illustrations in the header section of the website.","Can you sell stock illustrations?":"Can you sell stock illustrations?","If you are an artist and would like to sell your works of art, you can upload them to stock photography websites where your images will be available for purchase.":"If you are an artist and would like to sell your works of art, you can upload them to stock photography websites where your images will be available for purchase.","What’s the difference between individual and business plans?":"What’s the difference between individual and business plans?","\u003Ca href=\"%s\" class=\"%s\" %s\u003EPlans for individuals\u003C/a\u003E allow one person to download and use files. The individual license is suitable for freelancers, bloggers, sole proprietors, self-employed individuals, etc.":"\u003Ca href=\"%s\" class=\"%s\" %s\u003EPlans for individuals\u003C\u002Fa\u003E allow one person to download and use files. The individual license is suitable for freelancers, bloggers, sole proprietors, self-employed individuals, etc.","If you download images for use by a company, or plan to share files with a team, one of our business plans will be more suitable.":"If you download images for use by a company, or plan to share files with a team, one of our business plans will be more suitable.","\u003Ca href=\"%s\" class=\"%s\" %s\u003EBusiness plans\u003C/a\u003E grant your company a business license on files and provide you with convenient collaborative tools to create a license pool for your company.":"\u003Ca href=\"%s\" class=\"%s\" %s\u003EBusiness plans\u003C\u002Fa\u003E grant your company a business license on files and provide you with convenient collaborative tools to create a license pool for your company.","We can customize all of our plans to suit your needs. Contact us for pricing and more information.":"We can customize all of our plans to suit your needs. Contact us for pricing and more information.","What’s the difference between Standard and Extended licenses?":"What’s the difference between Standard and Extended licenses?","The \u003Ca href=\"%s\" class=\"%s\" %s\u003EStandard License\u003C/a\u003E is a default license type that allows you to use a downloaded file for personal and commercial purposes within the terms of the Standard License. \u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003EIt covers various use cases, including advertising and marketing, UI designs in websites and apps, product packaging, newspapers and magazines, book design, and more. \u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003EIf you have a Standard License, you can print no more than 500,000 copies of material created using a downloaded file. \u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003EThe \u003Ca href=\"%s\" class=\"%s\" %s\u003EExtended License\u003C/a\u003E permits all use cases that fall into the Standard License and have no limits regarding the number of printed copies. \u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003EThe Extended License allows you to use the downloaded files for resale or free distribution ( posters, postcards, cups, T-shirts, fabrics, or artworks). \u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003EThe Standard and Extended licenses can be purchased with Individual and Business plans.":"The \u003Ca href=\"%s\" class=\"%s\" %s\u003EStandard License\u003C\u002Fa\u003E is a default license type that allows you to use a downloaded file for personal and commercial purposes within the terms of the Standard License. \u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003EIt covers various use cases, including advertising and marketing, UI designs in websites and apps, product packaging, newspapers and magazines, book design, and more. \u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003EIf you have a Standard License, you can print no more than 500,000 copies of material created using a downloaded file. \u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003EThe \u003Ca href=\"%s\" class=\"%s\" %s\u003EExtended License\u003C\u002Fa\u003E permits all use cases that fall into the Standard License and have no limits regarding the number of printed copies. \u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003EThe Extended License allows you to use the downloaded files for resale or free distribution (posters, postcards, cups, T-shirts, fabrics, or artworks). \u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003EThe Standard and Extended licenses can be purchased with Individual and Business plans.","What types of files are included in a plan?":"What types of files are included in a plan?","With any of our \u003Ca href=\"%s\" class=\"%s\" %s\u003Eimage plans\u003C/a\u003E, you can download JPEG images of all sizes and vector images that can scale to any size. \u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\"%s\" class=\"%s\" %s\u003EVideo plans\u003C/a\u003E allow you to download videos of any resolution included in your purchased video plan. You can download SD, HD, and 4K videos with any of our subscriptions. Packs on videos offer files of a specific resolution: 240p, 480p, 720p, 1080p, or 4K. \u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003EAll of our \u003Ca href=\"%s\" class=\"%s\" %s\u003Eaudio plans\u003C/a\u003E provide you with access to our library of music and sound effects. A license on music purchased via monthly and yearly unlimited plans is only valid during the term of your subscription, or as long as your subscription auto-renews. Packs on music provide a lifelong license.":"With any of our \u003Ca href=\"%s\" class=\"%s\" %s\u003Eimage plans\u003C\u002Fa\u003E, you can download JPEG images of all sizes and vector images that can scale to any size. \u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\"%s\" class=\"%s\" %s\u003EVideo plans\u003C\u002Fa\u003E allow you to download videos of any resolution included in your purchased video plan. You can download SD, HD, and 4K videos with any of our subscriptions. Packs on videos offer files of a specific resolution: 240p, 480p, 720p, 1080p, or 4K. \u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003EAll of our \u003Ca href=\"%s\" class=\"%s\" %s\u003Eaudio plans\u003C\u002Fa\u003E provide you with access to our library of music and sound effects. A license on music purchased via monthly and yearly unlimited plans is only valid during the term of your subscription, or as long as your subscription auto-renews. Packs on music provide a lifelong license.","Should I purchase a subscription or a Pack?":"Should I purchase a subscription or a Pack?","\u003Cstrong\u003ESubscriptions\u003C/strong\u003E are the best fit for customers with an ongoing need for files. They provide you with a certain number of file downloads per month at the lowest prices.":"\u003Cstrong\u003ESubscriptions\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E are the best fit for customers with an ongoing need for files. They provide you with a certain number of file downloads per month at the lowest prices.","Image subscriptions roll over unused downloads to the following month for as long as your subscription auto-renews (except the 750 image/mo subscription).":"Image subscriptions roll over unused downloads to the following month for as long as your subscription auto-renews (except the 750 image\u002Fmo subscription).","Our audio subscription plans offer unlimited downloads.":"Our audio subscription plans offer unlimited downloads.","\u003Cstrong\u003EPacks\u003C/strong\u003E are tailored to customers who need a fixed number of downloads. They provide a set number of file downloads, and renew once you run out of them (until you cancel auto-renewal).":"\u003Cstrong\u003EPacks\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E are tailored to customers who need a fixed number of downloads. They provide a set number of file downloads, and renew once you run out of them (until you cancel auto-renewal).","If I don't use all of my downloads each month, will they carry over to the next month? Is there a limit to the number of downloads that can be carried over?":"If I don't use all of my downloads each month, will they carry over to the next month? Is there a limit to the number of downloads that can be carried over?","Yes, our image \u003Cstrong\u003Esubscriptions\u003C/strong\u003E roll over unused downloads to the following month for as long as your subscription auto-renews. (except the 750 image/mo subscription.) Unused downloads keep rolling over until the total reaches one year's worth.":"Yes, our image \u003Cstrong\u003Esubscriptions\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E roll over unused downloads to the following month for as long as your subscription auto-renews. (except the 750 image\u002Fmo subscription.) Unused downloads keep rolling over until the total reaches one year's worth.","Downloads within \u003Cstrong\u003EPacks\u003C/strong\u003E are available for a year after purchase. If you renew or purchase a new Pack before your billing period ends, the expiration date for unused Pack downloads is extended for one year.":"Downloads within \u003Cstrong\u003EPacks\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E are available for a year after purchase. If you renew or purchase a new Pack before your billing period ends, the expiration date for unused Pack downloads is extended for one year.","What happens if I cancel the auto-renewal of my plan?":"What happens if I cancel the auto-renewal of my plan?","There are no cancellation fees, unless you had purchased an annual subscription with monthly billing. In this case, you may be charged for any difference in price between monthly and annual monthly subscriptions.":"There are no cancelation fees, unless you had purchased an annual subscription with monthly billing. In this case, you may be charged for any difference in price between monthly and annual monthly subscriptions.","With all of our plans, you keep lifelong rights to use downloaded images regardless of your plan expiration date.":"With all of our plans, you keep lifelong rights to use downloaded images regardless of your plan expiration date.","Can I get a refund for my plan purchase?":"Can I get a refund for my plan purchase?","After purchasing a \u003Cstrong\u003Esubscription or Pack\u003C/strong\u003E, you have 30 days to change your mind and get a full refund. You are eligible for a refund if you have not downloaded any files.":"After purchasing a \u003Cstrong\u003Esubscription or Pack\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E, you have 30 days to change your mind and get a full refund. You are eligible for a refund if you have not downloaded any files.","Yes, our image \u003Cstrong\u003Esubscriptions\u003C/strong\u003E roll over unused downloads to the following month for as long as your subscription auto-renews. (except the %s image/mo subscription.) Unused downloads keep rolling over until the total reaches one year's worth.":"Yes, our image \u003Cstrong\u003Esubscriptions\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E roll over unused downloads to the following month for as long as your subscription auto-renews. (except the %s image\u002Fmo subscription.) Unused downloads keep rolling over until the total reaches one year's worth.","How does the API Background Remover work?":"How does the API Background Remover work?","The Background Remover is a tool developed by Depositphotos to help creatives spend less time on design routines. A user uploads an image to the tool’s page and gets a backgroundless visual in seconds. The Background Remover applies ever-improving algorithms to recognize objects in the foreground and apply smart blurring to bring you best possible results. The tool's application programming interface (API) integrates with your website or app using your exclusive key, allowing you to automate your workflow, offer your customers new services, and enable customers to remove image backgrounds without visiting Depositphotos.":"The Background Remover is a tool developed by DepositPhotos to help creatives spend less time on design routines. A user uploads an image to the tool’s page and gets a backgroundless visual in seconds. The Background Remover applies ever-improving algorithms to recognize objects in the foreground and apply smart blurring to bring you best possible results. \u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E The tool's application programming interface (API) integrates with your website or app using your exclusive key, allowing you to automate your workflow, offer your customers new services, and enable customers to remove image backgrounds without visiting DepositPhotos.","What is an API key?":"What is an API key?","An image background removal API key is a code we use to authenticate users and provide them with the services they request. You can use the same code for all of your apps and websites.":"An image background removal API key is a code we use to authenticate users and provide them with the services they request. You can use the same code for all of your apps and websites.","Can I use the background removal API on my platform for free?":"Can I use the background removal API on my platform for free?","There are three background removal API plans: Free Plan, Subscription Plan, and a customized Enterprise plan. The Free Plan allows you to get up to %s background-free images per month. No credit card details are needed to start this plan. If you are interested in automated AI-powered tools for processing videos, explore the Video Background Remover by Depositphotos.":"There are three background removal API plans: Free Plan, Subscription Plan, and a customized Enterprise plan. The Free Plan allows you to get up to %s background-free images per month. No credit card details are needed to start this plan. \u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E If you are interested in automated AI-powered tools for processing videos, explore the Video Background Remover by DepositPhotos.","How can I remove the background from my image programmatically?":"How can I remove the background from my image programmatically?","There are three BG remover plans: Free Plan, Subscription Plan, and a customized Enterprise Plan. The Free Plan allows you to get up to %s background-free images per month. It enables you to create MVPs with background remover integration and test your service ideas at a low cost. The plan works well for small businesses and startups. You can switch to Subscription anytime to scale your service for clients. If you are interested in automated AI-powered tools for processing videos, explore the Video Background Remover by Depositphotos.":"There are three BG remover plans: Free Plan, Subscription Plan, and a customized Enterprise Plan. The Free Plan allows you to get up to %s background-free images per month. It enables you to create MVPs with background remover integration and test your service ideas at a low cost. The plan works well for small businesses and startups. You can switch to Subscription anytime to scale your service for clients. \u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E If you are interested in automated AI-powered tools for processing videos, explore the Video Background Remover by DepositPhotos.","How can I integrate the Background Remover API?":"How can I integrate the Background Remover API?","Register on Depositphotos, select a background removal API plan that suits your needs, and get an API key. Use the key to connect your application or website and the Background Remover. Use the same key for any platform regardless of programming language. Try our Search by Image tool to speed up your design tasks further.":"Register on DepositPhotos, select a background removal API plan that suits your needs, and get an API key. Use the key to connect your application or website and the Background Remover. Use the same key for any platform regardless of programming language. Try our Search by Image tool to speed up your design tasks further.","How do users authenticate in the Background Remover API tool?":"How do users authenticate in the Background Remover API tool?","User authentication is done in the Background Remover API by using your exclusive key. Register or log in on the platform to get your unique API key and select a plan to use the tool. Your API key is unique so you shouldn’t share it with anyone outside your tech team.":"User authentication is done in the Background Remover API by using your exclusive key. Register or log in on the platform to get your unique API key and select a plan to use the tool. Your API key is unique so you shouldn’t share it with anyone outside your tech team.","What should I do if I want to switch to another API plan?":"What should I do if I want to switch to another API plan?","You can downgrade, upgrade, or cancel your background removal API plan anytime. Go to the “My Plans” section in your profile on Depositphotos to easily manage your plans.":"You can downgrade, upgrade, or cancel your background removal API plan anytime. Go to the “My Plans” section in your profile on DepositPhotos to easily manage your plans.","What file formats are supported by this API Background Remover?":"What file formats are supported by this API Background Remover?","The image background removal API can work with JPEG, JPG, PNG, and WEBP files.":"The image background removal API can work with JPEG, JPG, PNG, and WEBP files.","How does the background remover work?":"How does the background remover work?","The technology is based on neural networks. The algorithm analyzes your picture or video, distinguishes the foreground from the background, and isolates the main object(s).":"The technology is based on neural networks. The algorithm analyzes your picture or video, distinguishes the foreground from the background, and isolates the main object(s).","Can I remove backgrounds from images and videos for free?":"Can I remove backgrounds from images and videos for free?","Yes. With our free background remover, you can download medium-sized images or videos with backgrounds removed. To get HD files with transparent backgrounds, select a Background Remover plan.":"Yes. With our free background remover, you can download medium-sized images or videos with backgrounds removed. To get HD files with transparent backgrounds, select a Background Remover plan.","What files work best with this background removal tool?":"What files work best with this background removal tool?","The best results will come from images and videos with clearly defined subjects in the foreground. If there is no clear point of focus in the file, our AI may process it incorrectly. Generally, the tool works with all types of objects, but some very fine details might get cropped (e.g., flyaway hairs).":"The best results will come from images and videos with clearly defined subjects in the foreground. If there is no clear point of focus in the file, our AI may process it incorrectly. Generally, the tool works with all types of objects, but some very fine details might get cropped (e.g., flyaway hairs).","What file formats are supported?":"What file formats are supported by this background remover?","The Depositphotos background removal tool supports JPG, JPEG, PNG, and WEBP image formats and MP4, AVI, MOV, MPG, MPEG video formats for uploads. After removing the background, you can download your file in PNG or MP4 file format.":"The DepositPhotos background removal tool supports JPG, JPEG, PNG, and WEBP image formats and MP4, AVI, MOV, MPG, MPEG video formats for uploads. After removing the background, you can download your file in PNG or MP4 file format.","How does the video background remover work?":"How does the video background remover work?","To remove backgrounds from videos, upload your file to the tool’s page and wait for a couple of seconds. Then, see the results and download the new file to your device. \u003Cbr\u003E You can delete both green screen backgrounds or complicated ones. \u003Ca href=\"%s\" class=\"%s\" %s\u003ERemove backgrounds from images\u003C/a\u003E on Depositphotos too.":"To remove backgrounds from videos, upload your file to the tool’s page and wait for a couple of seconds. Then, see the results and download the new file to your device. \u003Cbr\u003E You can delete both green screen backgrounds or complicated ones. \u003Ca href=\"%s\" class=\"%s\" %s\u003ERemove backgrounds from images\u003C\u002Fa\u003E on DepositPhotos too.","Can I remove backgrounds from videos for free?":"How can I remove the background from a video?","Yes, you can. The video background remover is free for all registered users, regardless of their current plan. Free features for creatives include: \u003Ca href=\"%s\" class=\"%s\" %s\u003EImage Upscaler\u003C/a\u003E, \u003Ca href=\"%s\" class=\"%s\" %s\u003EImage Background Remover\u003C/a\u003E, \u003Ca href=\"%s\" class=\"%s\" %s\u003ESearch by Image\u003C/a\u003E, and the \u003Ca href=\"%s\" class=\"%s\" %s\u003EVistaCreate\u003C/a\u003E graphic editor (Starter).":"Go to the video background remover by DepositPhotos, upload your video, and get the background-free version in seconds. Other features for creatives include \u003Ca href=\"%s\" class=\"%s\" %s\u003EImage Upscaler\u003C\u002Fa\u003E, \u003Ca href=\"%s\" class=\"%s\" %s\u003EImage Background Remover\u003C\u002Fa\u003E, and \u003Ca href=\"%s\" class=\"%s\" %s\u003ESearch by Image\u003C\u002Fa\u003E.","What videos are best processed with the background remover?":"What videos are best processed with the background remover?","Videos with clearly defined objects in the foreground bring the best results when processing with our tool. \u003Cbr\u003E We continue to work on the tool’s algorithms to offer you an even better experience. Check out a similar product by Depositphotos — \u003Ca href=\"%s\" class=\"%s\" %s\u003EImage Background Remover\u003C/a\u003E, where you can edit results with brushes.":"Videos with clearly defined objects in the foreground bring the best results when processing with our tool. \u003Cbr\u003E We continue to work on the tool’s algorithms to offer you an even better experience. Check out a similar product by DepositPhotos — \u003Ca href=\"%s\" class=\"%s\" %s\u003EImage Background Remover\u003C\u002Fa\u003E, where you can edit results with brushes.","What formats does this video background remover support?":"What formats does this video background remover support?","The background remover video requirements are:":"The background remover video requirements are:","%s sec. max":"%s sec. max","How can I change my video background without a green screen?":"How can I change my video background without a green screen?","A green screen is not required if you’re planning to isolate objects over a transparent background. Upload your file to our video background remover online and enjoy the results in seconds.":"A green screen is not required if you’re planning to isolate objects over a transparent background. Upload your file to our video background remover online and enjoy the results in seconds.","How do I remove the white background from a video?":"How do I remove the white background from a video?","The Depositphotos tool automatically recognizes your video background and makes it transparent. Apply it to make the background transparent in videos shot against white or any definable backdrop.":"The DepositPhotos tool automatically recognizes your video background and makes it transparent. Apply it to make the background transparent in videos shot against white or any definable backdrop.","How do I get rid of a black background?":"How do I get rid of a black background?","Upload your file to the video background remover page and save the results to your device. With our tool, you can achieve clear backgrounds from various colors, including black, white, and green screen backgrounds.":"Upload your file to the video background remover page and save the results to your device. With our tool, you can achieve clear backgrounds from various colors, including black, white, and green screen backgrounds.","How does the photo enlarger and enhancer work?":"How does image upscaling work?","The Depositphotos image upscaler is completely AI-powered. Our neural network increases and enhances photos after recognizing objects. In order to enlarge images without losing quality, we trained our system on a huge dataset of visuals, and continue to do so. \u003Cbr\u003E At Depositphotos, we aim to provide you with useful tools that will help you save time for creative tasks. In addition to a free image upscaler, you can enjoy \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EBackground Remover\u003C/a\u003E, which automatically removes image backgrounds and works perfectly with enlarged images.":"The DepositPhotos image upscaler is completely AI-powered. Our neural network increases and enhances photos after recognizing objects. In order to enlarge images without losing quality, we trained our system on a huge dataset of visuals, and continue to do so. \u003Cbr\u003E At DepositPhotos, we aim to provide you with useful tools that will help you save time for creative tasks. In addition to a free image upscaler, you can enjoy \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EBackground Remover\u003C\u002Fa\u003E, which automatically removes image backgrounds and works perfectly with enlarged images.","Is the photo enhancer free to use?":"Is image upscaling AI-based?","Not all image upscaling tools are AI-based. The process can be done both manually and automatically. \u003Cbr\u003E In the first case, you need professional software to increase an image in size and enhance its resolution. This way, you have unlimited possibilities in regards to how large or high-quality an image becomes. However, these actions require design skills and extra time. Auto image upscaling tools are usually AI-based. For instance, the Depositphotos free image upscaler allows you to enlarge pictures twice in size, as well as increase their resolution and quality in one click. You just need to upload a visual to the website, wait a few seconds, and download its upscaled version. The same principle applies to similar AI-powered tools that allow you to \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Eremove backgrounds from videos\u003C/a\u003E and images for free.":"Not all image upscaling tools are AI-based. The process can be done both manually and automatically. \u003Cbr\u003E In the first case, you need professional software to increase an image in size and enhance its resolution. This way, you have unlimited possibilities in regards to how large or high-quality an image becomes. However, these actions require design skills and extra time. Auto image upscaling tools are usually AI-based. For instance, the DepositPhotos free image upscaler allows you to enlarge pictures twice in size, as well as increase their resolution and quality in one click. You just need to upload a visual to the website, wait a few seconds, and download its upscaled version. The same principle applies to similar AI-powered tools that allow you to \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Eremove backgrounds from videos\u003C\u002Fa\u003E and images for free.","Not all image upscaling tools are AI-based. The process can be done both manually and automatically. \u003Cbr\u003E In the first case, you need professional software to increase an image in size and enhance its resolution. This way, you have unlimited possibilities in regards to how large or high-quality an image becomes. However, these actions require design skills and extra time. Auto image upscaling tools are usually AI-based. For instance, the Depositphotos free image upscaler allows you to enlarge pictures twice in size, as well as increase their resolution and quality in one click. You just need to upload a visual to the website, wait a few seconds, and download its upscaled version. The same principle applies to similar AI-powered tool that allow you to remove background from images for free.":"Not all image upscaling tools are AI-based. The process can be done both manually and automatically. \u003Cbr\u003E In the first case, you need professional software to increase an image in size and enhance its resolution. This way, you have unlimited possibilities in regards to how large or high-quality an image becomes. However, these actions require design skills and extra time. Auto image upscaling tools are usually AI-based. For instance, the DepositPhotos free image upscaler allows you to enlarge pictures twice in size, as well as increase their resolution and quality in one click. You just need to upload a visual to the website, wait a few seconds, and download its upscaled version. The same principle applies to similar AI-powered tool that allow you to remove background from images for free.","How do I increase my image’s resolution if there are overexposed objects with many details?":"How can I upscale pictures for free?","Our image quality enhancer generates missing pixel data and enlarges photos with no loss of quality. The fewer informative pixels are there, the harder it is to upscale images. The AI-powered image resizer works well with detailed images.":"You can enlarge photos for free with the help of DepositPhotos image upscaler. The tool allows you to process any number of photos, whether you need to edit one or dozens during a short period of time.","What file formats are supported by the image enhancer?":"Does upscaling improve picture quality?","Resize JPG (or JPEG) files with this free online tool, then download your image in the same file format.":"Yes, when you upscale an image with the DepositPhotos tool, neural networks automatically reconstruct pixels to increase picture size and resolution.","How can I change picture size?":"How do you upscale the quality of an image?","You can resize an image to twice its size.":"It is quick and easy with the help of the free DepositPhotos image upscaler. All you need to do is to upload a picture, let our smart algorithms automatically enhance it, and download a high-quality result in a couple of seconds.","Can AI enhance images?":"Can AI enhance images?","Yes, AI can be taught to enhance images according to specific requirements. For instance, the Depositphotos image upscaler allows enhancing image quality and resolution, while also enlarging it twice in size.":"Yes, AI can be taught to enhance images according to specific requirements. For instance, the DepositPhotos image upscaler allows enhancing image quality and resolution, while also enlarging it twice in size.","Can you increase image resolution without losing quality?":"Can you increase image resolution without losing quality?","Yes, with the help of AI-based tools like the Depositphotos image upscaler, file size and resolution can be increased along with its quality. The tool’s smart algorithms reconstruct missing pixels when enlarging an image, enhancing all parameters for the best possible result.":"Yes, with the help of AI-based tools like the DepositPhotos image upscaler, file size and resolution can be increased along with its quality. The tool’s smart algorithms reconstruct missing pixels when enlarging an image, enhancing all parameters for the best possible result.","How can I increase image resolution for free?":"How can I increase image resolution for free?","You can increase the resolution of photos, vectors, and illustrations for free with the help of the Depositphotos image upscaler. Or, you can do it manually using paid, professional software for image editing and post-processing.":"You can increase the resolution of photos, vectors, and illustrations for free with the help of the DepositPhotos image upscaler. Or, you can do it manually using paid, professional software for image editing and post-processing.","What other useful tools does Depositphotos have to work with images?":"What other useful tools does DepositPhotos have to work with images?","In addition to image and video upscalers, you can find the \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EReverse Image Search\u003C/a\u003E tool that allows you to find high-quality and royalty-free versions of photos, vectors, or illustrations you like.":"In addition to image and video upscalers, you can find the \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EReverse Image Search\u003C\u002Fa\u003E tool that allows you to find high-quality and royalty-free versions of photos, vectors, or illustrations you like.","How do I search with an image?":"How can I search for images online?","You can use platforms like Google or the search bar on stock content platforms like Depositphotos. The first approach leads to almost infinite results; however, you can’t integrate most of them into your projects due to copyright issues. \u003Cbr\u003E All images on Depositphotos are royalty-free, which means you can download them within your plan and use them without personal permission from their authors. You can also apply our \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Eimage background remover\u003C/a\u003E to get background-free versions.":"You can use platforms like Google or the search bar on stock content platforms like DepositPhotos. The first approach leads to almost infinite results; however, you can’t integrate most of them into your projects due to copyright issues. \u003Cbr\u003E All images on DepositPhotos are royalty-free, which means you can download them within your plan and use them without personal permission from their authors. You can also apply our \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Eimage background remover\u003C\u002Fa\u003E to get background-free versions.","How do I search for an image?":"What is reverse image search?","Reverse image search means you search for pictures using another picture (instead of keywords). \u003Cbr\u003E On Google, a reverse image search can help you track the origin of your picture. On Depositphotos, the tool provides you with content you can use for your commercial or personal needs. \u003Cbr\u003E A free reverse image search saves time, as you instantly find what you are looking for. Another Depositphotos tool to reach this goal is \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Evideo background remover\u003C/a\u003E, which allows you to skip manual video editing.":"Reverse image search means you search for pictures using another picture (instead of keywords). \u003Cbr\u003E On Google, a reverse image search can help you track the origin of your picture. On DepositPhotos, the tool provides you with content you can use for your commercial or personal needs. \u003Cbr\u003E A free reverse image search saves time, as you instantly find what you are looking for. Another DepositPhotos tool to reach this goal is \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Evideo background remover\u003C\u002Fa\u003E, which allows you to skip manual video editing.","Reverse image search means you search for pictures using another picture (instead of keywords). \u003Cbr\u003E On Google, a reverse image search can help you track the origin of your picture. On Depositphotos, the tool provides you with content you can use for your commercial or personal needs. \u003Cbr\u003E A free reverse image search saves time, as you instantly find what you are looking for.":"Reverse image search means you search for pictures using another picture (instead of keywords). \u003Cbr\u003E On Google, a reverse image search can help you track the origin of your picture. On DepositPhotos, the tool provides you with content you can use for your commercial or personal needs. \u003Cbr\u003E A free reverse image search saves time, as you instantly find what you are looking for.","What if Depositphotos can’t find any results for my image?":"How does the reverse image search engine work?","If you have a reference image, click on the “photo camera” icon in the Depositphotos search bar and share it as a file or URL. \u003Cbr\u003E An AI-powered algorithm recognizes objects in your image and finds identical or similar visuals in the Depositphotos library. Download them to use in your commercial and personal projects. \u003Cbr\u003E Search by Image is a free tool in our ecosystem for creatives. Explore our \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Efree image upscaler\u003C/a\u003E to optimize your production budget even more.":"If you have a reference image, click on the “photo camera” icon in the DepositPhotos search bar and share it as a file or URL. \u003Cbr\u003E An AI-powered algorithm recognizes objects in your image and finds identical or similar visuals in the DepositPhotos library. Download them to use in your commercial and personal projects. \u003Cbr\u003E Search by Image is a free tool in our ecosystem for creatives. Explore our \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Efree image upscaler\u003C\u002Fa\u003E to optimize your production budget even more.","Why do you need to search by image?":"Why do you need to search by image?","A reverse image search tool works well for tracking picture origin (for example, to detect fakes) and identifying plagiarized content. \u003Cbr\u003E The tool helps you find licensed images for projects or enjoy royalty-free content similar to images by authors you like. \u003Cbr\u003E If you have an image you downloaded a long time ago, but need an improved full-resolution and watermark-free version, upload it to the search bar to get ready-to-use high-quality content.":"A reverse image search tool works well for tracking picture origin (for example, to detect fakes) and identifying plagiarized content. \u003Cbr\u003E The tool helps you find licensed images for projects or enjoy royalty-free content similar to images by authors you like. \u003Cbr\u003E If you have an image you downloaded a long time ago, but need an improved full-resolution and watermark-free version, upload it to the search bar to get ready-to-use high-quality content.","How do you reverse image search without Google?":"How do you reverse image search without Google?","You can find a similar image to the one you like with illustrations and photo reverse search on Depositphotos. Our platform leverages AI to provide you with the best possible results, even if there is no identical image in our library. Moreover, you can download any image you like under your plan and use it in your projects.":"You can find a similar image to the one you like with illustrations and photo reverse search on DepositPhotos. Our platform leverages AI to provide you with the best possible results, even if there is no identical image in our library. Moreover, you can download any image you like under your plan and use it in your projects.","How do I search by image on Depositphotos?":"How do I search by image on DepositPhotos?","Use an image file (JPG, PNG, WEBP, BMP, or TIFF; 10MB max) as a reference or paste a URL to find similar royalty-free images on Depositphotos. You can find similar photos, vectors, or illustrations by going to the “Tools” section on the top Depositphotos menu, or by clicking on the “photo” icon in the Depositphotos main search bar.":"Use an image file (JPG, PNG, WEBP, BMP, or TIFF; 10MB max) as a reference or paste a URL to find similar royalty-free images on DepositPhotos. You can find similar photos, vectors, or illustrations by going to the “Tools” section on the top DepositPhotos menu, or by clicking on the “photo” icon in the DepositPhotos main search bar.","Can you reverse image search screenshots?":"Can you reverse image search screenshots?","You are welcome to search by image online using screenshots, small pictures, and watermarked images. If you want to find a high-resolution, licensed version of an image you found on another website, copy the URL and paste it into our search by image tool.":"You are welcome to search by image online using screenshots, small pictures, and watermarked images. If you want to find a high-resolution, licensed version of an image you found on another website, copy the URL and paste it into our search by image tool.","How do you reverse image search on a phone?":"How do you reverse image search on a phone?","Search by image using references from your mobile storage. To apply the tool to images received through messages, save them onto your device and then upload them to the search bar on Depositphotos (click the “photo camera” icon to switch to the needed mode). \u003Cbr\u003E Instead of using a reference image file, you can also find similar images through your smartphone by copying an image URL and pasting it.":"Search by image using references from your mobile storage. To apply the tool to images received through messages, save them onto your device and then upload them to the search bar on DepositPhotos (click the “photo camera” icon to switch to the needed mode). \u003Cbr\u003E Instead of using a reference image file, you can also find similar images through your smartphone by copying an image URL and pasting it.","How does the referral program work?":"How does the referral program work?","Every time you invite a new friend, you get a 40% cash reward from their first purchase and 15% from their next ones for 3 years. The term starts from the moment you receive a notification about the referral being successful.":"Every time you invite a new friend, you get a 40% cash reward from their first purchase and 15% from their next ones for 3 years. The term starts from the moment you receive a notification about the referral being successful.","Is the referral program only available to new users?":"Is the referral program only available to new users?","To participate in the referral program, you have to be registered on Depositphotos. You will receive your referral bonus whether or not your plan is active. However, the friend you invite through your referral link should be new to Depositphotos and must use your link to create an account and purchase any available plan.":"To participate in the referral program, you have to be registered on DepositPhotos. You will receive your referral bonus whether or not your plan is active. However, the friend you invite through your referral link should be new to DepositPhotos and must use your link to create an account and purchase any available plan.","When do I get paid for a successful referral?":"When do I get paid for a successful referral?","The referral reward will appear in your account immediately after the person you’ve invited makes a purchase. However, you can withdraw your reward one month after the moment of purchase and as soon as it reaches $50.":"The referral reward will appear in your account immediately after the person you’ve invited makes a purchase. However, you can withdraw your reward one month after the moment of purchase and as soon as it reaches $50.","Can I redirect my friends to different pages on the Depositphotos website?":"Can I redirect my friends to different pages on the DepositPhotos website?","The initial unique referral link will redirect your friends to the Depositphotos home page. However, you can share a different Depositphotos page as your referral link. To do so, copy your account ID (“?ref=XXXXXXXX”) and append it to the desired URL.":"The initial unique referral link will redirect your friends to the DepositPhotos home page. However, you can share a different DepositPhotos page as your referral link. To do so, copy your account ID (“?ref=XXXXXXXX”) and append it to the desired URL.","What images can I use for free?":"What images can I use for free?","Images from the Free Files collection are all free to use for personal and business goals. To find free images or other files, limit your search to them with the main search bar on Depositphotos (select “Free” in the drop down menu before the keyword field), or go directly to the \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\"\u003EFree File search\u003C/a\u003E. Then, apply advanced filters from the menu on the left to save time.":"Images from the Free Files collection are all free to use for personal and business goals. To find free images or other files, limit your search to them with the main search bar on DepositPhotos (select “Free” in the drop down menu before the keyword field), or go directly to the \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\"\u003EFree File search\u003C\u002Fa\u003E. Then, apply advanced filters from the menu on the left to save time.","How do I know if I can use an image for free?":"How do I know if I can use an image for free?","In your search results, all free images have a green label with the word “Free”. Hover over a file preview to see it. You can also get to the Free File collection from the top menu (select “Images” and then “Free Images”). All images there are free.":"In your search results, all free images have a green label with the word “Free”. Hover over a file preview to see it. You can also get to the Free File collection from the top menu (select “Images” and then “Free Images”). All images there are free.","Are free images copyright free?":"Are free images copyright free?","No, free images are not copyright-free. All images and videos offered within Free Files are available under the\u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\"\u003EAttributed Free License Agreement\u003C/a\u003E and can be used only with proper attribution. You can't resell or distribute them for free; the maximum number of printed copies allowed is 500,000.":"No, free images are not copyright-free. All images and videos offered within Free Files are available under the \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\"\u003EAttributed Free License Agreement\u003C\u002Fa\u003E and can be used only with proper attribution. You can't resell or distribute them for free; the maximum number of printed copies allowed is 500,000.","Can I use free images for commercial purposes?":"Can I use free images for commercial purposes?","Yes, you can use our free stock images for commercial, editorial, or personal creative projects, as well as for derivative works. All files are subject to the rules specified in the \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\"\u003EAttributed Free License Agreement\u003C/a\u003E.":"Yes, you can use our free stock images for commercial, editorial, or personal creative projects, as well as for derivative works. All files are subject to the rules specified in the \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\"\u003EAttributed Free License Agreement\u003C\u002Fa\u003E.","Where can I download images for free? Where can I find free images?":"Where can I download images for free? Where can I find free images?","On Depositphotos, search for free photos and other files using the main search bar, or go directly to the Free Files collection and search there. In the general search results, free photos, vectors, and other files have a special “Free” label.\u003Cbr\u003EAdvanced searching tools such as Color, Orientation, Date Added, Portraiture, or other search filters are available for all Depositphotos users. \u003Cbr\u003EWe frequently use our Free Files to give you access to new and trending content. Add any free stock photo, vector image, or video to Favorites and avoid losing them.":"On DepositPhotos, search for free photos and other files using the main search bar, or go directly to the Free Files collection and search there. In the general search results, free photos, vectors, and other files have a special “Free” label. \u003Cbr\u003EAdvanced searching tools such as Color, Orientation, Date Added, Portraiture, or other search filters are available for all DepositPhotos users.\u003Cbr\u003EWe frequently use our Free Files to give you access to new and trending content. Add any free stock photo, vector image, or video to Favorites and avoid losing them.","How can I use free images and videos I download from Depositphotos?":"How can I use free images and videos I download from DepositPhotos?","You can use free stock video and images for commercial and educational purposes, as well as derivative works. Files are allowed to be used for digital and print if there are less than 50,000 copies. It’s prohibited to resell free stock videos and pictures, or distribute them for free.\u003Cbr\u003EExamples of permitted use: sites, advertising banners, digital wallpapers, covers, as well as illustrations for books, flyers, and more.":"You can use free stock video and images for commercial and educational purposes, as well as derivative works. Files are allowed to be used for digital and print if there are less than 500,000 copies. It’s prohibited to resell free stock videos and pictures, or distribute them for free.\u003Cbr\u003EExamples of permitted use: sites, advertising banners, digital wallpapers, covers, as well as illustrations for books, flyers, and more.","How do you give attribution to an image?":"How do you give attribution to an image?","When using a Free File, you must take all possible and reasonable efforts to credit the copyright owner (Depositphotos contributor), give attribution to Depositphotos and post a link to https://www.depositphotos.com (if applicable). The copyright notice must contain the following: \"[Name or Nickname of the Contributor (author)] /Depositphotos.com\". \u003Cbr\u003E Alternatively, at your discretion, you may provide a direct link to the free file on the Depositphotos website, which will also be considered a correctly performed attribution.":"When using a Free File, you must take all possible and reasonable efforts to credit the copyright owner (DepositPhotos contributor), give attribution to DepositPhotos and post a link to https:\u002F\u002Fwww.DepositPhotos.com (if applicable). The copyright notice must contain the following: \"[Name or Nickname of the Contributor (author)] \u002FDepositPhotos.com\". \u003Cbr\u003E Alternatively, at your discretion, you may provide a direct link to the free file on the DepositPhotos website, which will also be considered a correctly performed attribution.","How often are new free images added to the site?":"How often are new free images added to the site?","New free stock images are added to the Depositphotos library weekly. Subscribe to our newsletter to receive weekly free file updates.":"New free stock images are added to the DepositPhotos library weekly. Subscribe to our newsletter to receive weekly free file updates.","How does the AI Image Generator work?":"How does the AI Image Generator work?","The AI Image Generator takes your text prompts and turns them into visuals. There are two ways to work with it:":"The AI Image Generator takes your text prompts and turns them into visuals. There are two ways to work with it:","\u003Cstrong\u003EText only:\u003C/strong\u003E Describe the image you want, choose an aspect ratio and style, then click “Generate”.":"\u003Cstrong\u003EText only:\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E Describe the image you want, choose an aspect ratio and style, then click “Generate”.","\u003Cstrong\u003EText + visual reference:\u003C/strong\u003E To get results faster, combine a text prompt with an uploaded image and adjust the match strength.":"\u003Cstrong\u003EText + visual reference:\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E To get results faster, combine a text prompt with an uploaded image and adjust the match strength.","In both cases, you’ll receive four unique visuals ready to use in your projects. You can download your favorite or save them all.":"In both cases, you’ll receive four unique visuals ready to use in your projects. You can download your favorite or save them all.","How are AI-generated images made?":"How are AI-generated images made?","The AI Image Generator uses smart algorithms to transform text prompts into unique visuals.":"The AI Image Generator uses smart algorithms to transform text prompts into unique visuals.","Our holistic AI solution, developed in partnership with \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EBria.ai\u003C/a\u003E, is trained on large datasets of images paired with detailed descriptions. When the AI Image Generator receives a text prompt, it uses its knowledge to interpret the words, identify patterns, and combine them into a new image that fits the description. The process typically begins with random noise, which the AI gradually refines step by step until a clear picture appears.":"Our holistic AI solution, developed in partnership with \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EBria.ai\u003C\u002Fa\u003E, is trained on large datasets of images paired with detailed descriptions. When the AI Image Generator receives a text prompt, it uses its knowledge to interpret the words, identify patterns, and combine them into a new image that fits the description. The process typically begins with random noise, which the AI gradually refines step by step until a clear picture appears.","Can I download the generated images multiple times?":"Can I download the generated images multiple times?","Yes, you can download images created with the AI Generator as many times as you need. You can find them, as well as all your previous downloads, in your DepositPhotos account.":"Yes, you can download images created with the AI Generator as many times as you need. You can find them, as well as all your previous downloads, in your DepositPhotos account.","Can I use AI-generated images for commercial purposes?":"Can I use AI-generated images for commercial purposes?","Images created with the AI Generator are provided under the \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EStandard license\u003C/a\u003E, giving you lifelong rights to use them for personal or commercial purposes. Since our model is trained on commercially licensed data, the images won’t contain copyrighted logos or protected objects. This ensures you can confidently use them in your projects without worrying about copyright issues.":"Images created with the AI Generator are provided under the \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EStandard license\u003C\u002Fa\u003E, giving you lifelong rights to use them for personal or commercial purposes. Since our model is trained on commercially licensed data, the images won’t contain copyrighted logos or protected objects. This ensures you can confidently use them in your projects without worrying about copyright issues.","Which types of projects are best suited for DepositPhotos AI-generated visuals?":"Which types of projects are best suited for DepositPhotos AI-generated visuals?","\u003Cstrong\u003EDepositPhotos AI Generator applications\u003C/strong\u003E cover a wide range of digital and print projects. \u003Cstrong\u003EBest AI design use cases\u003C/strong\u003E include:":"\u003Cstrong\u003EDepositPhotos AI Generator applications\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E cover a wide range of digital and print projects. \u003Cstrong\u003EBest AI design use cases\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E include:","\u003Cstrong\u003EDigital:\u003C/strong\u003E websites, advertising banners, emails, presentations, e-books, videos, TV ads, software, unofficial logos, personal use, and more.":"\u003Cstrong\u003EDigital:\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E websites, advertising banners, emails, presentations, e-books, videos, TV ads, software, unofficial logos, personal use, and more.","\u003Cstrong\u003EPrint:\u003C/strong\u003E ads in newspapers and magazines, printed advertising materials, business cards, flyers, labels and product packaging, book covers, and more.":"\u003Cstrong\u003EPrint:\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E ads in newspapers and magazines, printed advertising materials, business cards, flyers, labels and product packaging, book covers, and more.","Are generated images exclusive, and what rights do businesses get?":"Are generated images exclusive, and what rights do businesses get?","With each prompt, you get \u003Cstrong\u003Eexclusive AI images\u003C/strong\u003E licensed solely for you. This means generated visuals won’t be added to our stock library or become available to other users.":"With each prompt, you get \u003Cstrong\u003Eexclusive AI images\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E licensed solely for you. This means generated visuals won’t be added to our stock library or become available to other users.","Since images created with the AI Generator are covered by the \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EStandard License\u003C/a\u003E, businesses receive lifelong \u003Cstrong\u003Eimage licensing rights\u003C/strong\u003E for commercial use in both print and digital projects. The license allows unlimited digital usage and up to 500,000 printed copies or impressions. You can include AI-generated visuals in items for resale or free distribution, as long as the image plays only a minor role.":"Since images created with the AI Generator are covered by the \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EStandard License\u003C\u002Fa\u003E, businesses receive lifelong \u003Cstrong\u003Eimage licensing rights\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E for commercial use in both print and digital projects. The license allows unlimited digital usage and up to 500,000 printed copies or impressions. You can include AI-generated visuals in items for resale or free distribution, as long as the image plays only a minor role.","What can you do with visuals created using a text-to-image generator? Can I edit the generated AI images?":"What can you do with visuals created using a text-to-image generator? Can I edit the generated AI images?","You can use AI-generated images directly in your \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Emarketing campaigns\u003C/a\u003E or refine them to suit specific needs. DepositPhotos provides a set of advanced \u003Cstrong\u003EAI design tools\u003C/strong\u003E that make image editing effortless:":"You can use AI-generated images directly in your \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Emarketing campaigns\u003C\u002Fa\u003E or refine them to suit specific needs. DepositPhotos provides a set of advanced \u003Cstrong\u003EAI design tools\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E that make image editing effortless:","\u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EBackground Remover\u003C/a\u003E erases backgrounds with precision":"\u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EBackground Remover\u003C\u002Fa\u003E erases backgrounds with precision","\u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EImage Upscaler\u003C/a\u003E enhances resolution while preserving quality":"\u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EImage Upscaler\u003C\u002Fa\u003E enhances resolution while preserving quality","\u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EVistaCreate\u003C/a\u003E enables professional-grade design for web and print":"\u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EVistaCreate\u003C\u002Fa\u003E enables professional-grade design for web and print","Can I create complete designs with AI?":"Can I create complete designs with AI?","Absolutely! The combined power of the AI Image Generator and \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EVistaCreate\u003C/a\u003E allows you to streamline content production and craft custom web or print designs in minutes.":"Absolutely! The combined power of the AI Image Generator and \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EVistaCreate\u003C\u002Fa\u003E allows you to streamline content production and craft custom web or print designs in minutes.","Here’s how to do it step by step:":"Here’s how to do it step by step:","Create visuals tailored to your audience or campaign.":"Create visuals tailored to your audience or campaign.","Open the VistaCreate editor and select a design template you like.":"Open the VistaCreate editor and select a design template you like.","Upload your generated image and integrate it into the design.":"Upload your generated image and integrate it into the design.","Customize the design, then download it once it matches your vision.":"Customize the design, then download it once it matches your vision.","What advanced editing tools are available?":"What advanced editing tools are available?","You can access powerful editing tools, including \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EBackground Remover\u003C/a\u003E, \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EImage Upscaler\u003C/a\u003E, and the \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EVistaCreate design editor\u003C/a\u003E. Plus, with the \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EAI Art Generator\u003C/a\u003E, you can create dreamy, imaginative, or fantastic scenes, perfect for campaigns that call for a more artistic touch. Select the “Art” style when generating images to achieve these results.":"You can access powerful editing tools, including \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EBackground Remover\u003C\u002Fa\u003E, \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EImage Upscaler\u003C\u002Fa\u003E, and the \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EVistaCreate design editor\u003C\u002Fa\u003E. Plus, with the \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EAI Art Generator\u003C\u002Fa\u003E, you can create dreamy, imaginative, or fantastic scenes, perfect for campaigns that call for a more artistic touch. Select the “Art” style when generating images to achieve these results.","How do you create a prompt?":"How do you create a prompt?","You can \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Ecreate a strong prompt\u003C/a\u003E by describing your ideal image in detail. For results that match your imagination, follow this \u003Cstrong\u003Eprompt writing guide\u003C/strong\u003E:":"You can \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Ecreate a strong prompt\u003C\u002Fa\u003E by describing your ideal image in detail. For results that match your imagination, follow this \u003Cstrong\u003Eprompt writing guide\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E:","In the text box, provide a comprehensive image description, specifying elements like subject, colors, lighting, and mood.":"In the text box, provide a comprehensive image description, specifying elements like subject, colors, lighting, and mood.","Highlight important details with adjectives such as \"bright and cheerful” or \"warm and cozy.\"":"Highlight important details with adjectives such as \"bright and cheerful” or \"warm and cozy.\"","Clarify relationships between subjects or the overall atmosphere (e.g., “two friends laughing” or “a dog walking in a sunny park”) to add context.":"Clarify relationships between subjects or the overall atmosphere (e.g., “two friends laughing” or “a dog walking in a sunny park”) to add context.","Define composition (layout, orientation, focal points) and aesthetic (e.g, realistic, futuristic, dreamy).":"Define composition (layout, orientation, focal points) and aesthetic (e.g, realistic, futuristic, dreamy).","How do I write effective prompts for the best AI-generated results?":"How do I write effective prompts for the best AI-generated results?","The most effective \u003Cstrong\u003EAI image generation tips\u003C/strong\u003E emphasize using detailed and specific prompts. The more information you provide, the closer the AI Image Generator will match your vision.":"The most effective \u003Cstrong\u003EAI image generation tips\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E emphasize using detailed and specific prompts. The more information you provide, the closer the AI Image Generator will match your vision.","When writing the prompt, be sure to specify:":"When writing the prompt, be sure to specify:","\u003Cstrong\u003ESubject:\u003C/strong\u003E people, animals, characters, objects, etc.":"\u003Cstrong\u003ESubject:\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E people, animals, characters, objects, etc.","\u003Cstrong\u003ESetting:\u003C/strong\u003E city, park, beach, photo studio, etc.":"\u003Cstrong\u003ESetting:\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E city, park, beach, photo studio, etc.","\u003Cstrong\u003EAttributes:\u003C/strong\u003E colors, lighting, angles, and other details.":"\u003Cstrong\u003EAttributes:\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E colors, lighting, angles, and other details.","\u003Cstrong\u003EStyle or mood:\u003C/strong\u003E photorealistic, surreal, dramatic, dreamy, etc.":"\u003Cstrong\u003EStyle or mood:\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E photorealistic, surreal, dramatic, dreamy, etc.","Although the DepositPhotos AI Generator supports multiple languages, we recommend writing prompts in English for the most accurate results.":"Although the DepositPhotos AI Generator supports multiple languages, we recommend writing prompts in English for the most accurate results.","Does DepositPhotos accept content made with AI image generators?":"Does DepositPhotos accept content made with AI image generators?","DepositPhotos prioritizes human-created content. Currently, \u003Cstrong\u003EAI-generated content acceptance\u003C/strong\u003E from contributors is not supported on the platform.":"DepositPhotos prioritizes human-created content. Currently, \u003Cstrong\u003EAI-generated content acceptance\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E from contributors is not supported on the platform.","What subscription or plan is required to access the DepositPhotos AI tool?":"What subscription or plan is required to access the DepositPhotos AI tool?","We don’t offer separate \u003Cstrong\u003EAI subscription plans\u003C/strong\u003E. To access the AI Image Generator, simply purchase any \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EDepositPhotos plan\u003C/a\u003E. We provide affordable subscriptions and flexible file packs for both individuals and companies. Once you have a plan, you can generate unlimited images and download them within your available file limit.":"We don’t offer separate \u003Cstrong\u003EAI subscription plans\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E. To access the AI Image Generator, simply purchase any \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EDepositPhotos plan\u003C\u002Fa\u003E. We provide affordable subscriptions and flexible file packs for both individuals and companies. Once you have a plan, you can generate unlimited images and download them within your available file limit.","What subscription or plan options are available for corporate teams?":"What subscription or plan options are available for corporate teams?","\u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ECorporate AI plan options\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/a\u003E include subscriptions and packs. With any business plan—whether for images, videos, or music—you’ll get unlimited AI generations, a business license for files, and convenient collaborative tools. If you need a tailored solution, we can customize any plan to suit your needs.":"\u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ECorporate AI plan options\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E\u003C\u002Fa\u003E include subscriptions and packs. With any business plan—whether for images, videos, or music—you’ll get unlimited AI generations, a business license for files, and convenient collaborative tools. If you need a tailored solution, we can customize any plan to suit your needs.","What safety and ethical guidelines are applied to AI outputs?":"What safety and ethical guidelines are applied to AI outputs?","When developing our AI solution in partnership with \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EBria\u003C/a\u003E, we followed \u003Cstrong\u003Eethical AI guidelines\u003C/strong\u003E prioritizing safety, fairness, accountability, and privacy.":"When developing our AI solution in partnership with \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EBria\u003C\u002Fa\u003E, we followed \u003Cstrong\u003Eethical AI guidelines\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E prioritizing safety, fairness, accountability, and privacy.","To support \u003Cstrong\u003Eresponsible AI generation\u003C/strong\u003E, we encourage you to use the DepositPhotos AI Generator ethically. Please avoid creating images that:":"To support \u003Cstrong\u003Eresponsible AI generation\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E, we encourage you to use the DepositPhotos AI Generator ethically. Please avoid creating images that:","Could be considered deceptive, hateful, threatening, unethical, or discriminatory.":"Could be considered deceptive, hateful, threatening, unethical, or discriminatory.","Suggest endorsement of political parties, impersonate another person, promote illegal drugs, or involve illegal gambling and arms trafficking.":"Suggest endorsement of political parties, impersonate another person, promote illegal drugs, or involve illegal gambling and arms trafficking.","Infringe on third-party copyright or trade secrets, violate laws, or are otherwise fraudulent or malicious.":"Infringe on third-party copyright or trade secrets, violate laws, or are otherwise fraudulent or malicious.","How do you keep content safe?":"How do you keep content safe?","To ensure \u003Cstrong\u003EAI content safety\u003C/strong\u003E, we train our system exclusively on commercially licensed data. This approach provides users with \u003Cstrong\u003Esecure AI images\u003C/strong\u003E that are free of copyrighted logos, objects, or other elements that could cause infringement. All AI-generated files remain private—they will not be added to our library or shared with other users.":"To ensure \u003Cstrong\u003EAI content safety\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E, we train our system exclusively on commercially licensed data. This approach provides users with \u003Cstrong\u003Esecure AI images\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E that are free of copyrighted logos, objects, or other elements that could cause infringement. All AI-generated files remain private—they will not be added to our library or shared with other users.","Can I upload a reference image to guide the AI’s output?":"Can I upload a reference image to guide the AI’s output?","Sure! Our tool supports \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Ereference-based image generation\u003C/a\u003E, helping you achieve the perfect result faster.":"Sure! Our tool supports \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Ereference-based image generation\u003C\u002Fa\u003E, helping you achieve the perfect result faster.","How to use this feature:":"How to use this feature:","Type your prompt in the generator’s text box":"Type your prompt in the generator’s text box","Upload a reference image":"Upload a reference image","Adjust the match strength":"Adjust the match strength","Review the generated visuals and download your favorite":"Review the generated visuals and download your favorite","Does the AI Image Generator create copyrighted images?":"Does the AI Image Generator create copyrighted images?","Copyright law traditionally protects works created exclusively by human authors. This means image generators cannot produce copyrighted outputs. However, when you use the DepositPhotos AI Image Generator, you receive \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Elicensed AI content\u003C/a\u003E that is exclusively yours and will not be available for others.":"Copyright law traditionally protects works created exclusively by human authors. This means image generators cannot produce copyrighted outputs. However, when you use the DepositPhotos AI Image Generator, you receive \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003Elicensed AI content\u003C\u002Fa\u003E that is exclusively yours and will not be available for others.","What is an AI design assistant?":"What is an AI design assistant?","The DepositPhotos AI Assistant is a powerful tool that lets users perform a wide range of creative tasks:":"The DepositPhotos AI Assistant is a powerful tool that lets users perform a wide range of creative tasks:","Find images, videos, or audio files in the %sM+ library.":"Find images, videos, or audio files in the %sM+ library.","Generate unique visuals suitable for commercial use.":"Generate unique visuals suitable for commercial use.","Adjust images by upscaling, resizing, removing backgrounds, and more.":"Adjust images by upscaling, resizing, removing backgrounds, and more.","Discover creative ideas for any campaign.":"Discover creative ideas for any campaign.","The AI design assistant brings the entire creative process into one streamlined workflow, so users don’t need to switch between multiple standalone tools.":"The AI design assistant brings the entire creative process into one streamlined workflow, so users don’t need to switch between multiple standalone tools.","Is AI-generated design safe for commercial use?":"Is AI-generated design safe for commercial use?","AI-generated designs can be safe for commercial use if you choose secure AI design tools or software with clear licensing terms.":"AI-generated designs can be safe for commercial use if you choose secure AI design tools or software with clear licensing terms.","The DepositPhotos AI Assistant connects AI tools with a library of licensed assets, helping users find or generate visuals suitable for marketing, websites, and presentations. Here, you can create images that are safe for commercial use. Our AI Generator is trained only on licensed, ethically sourced content and follows clear rules to respect intellectual property, ensuring reliable results.":"The DepositPhotos AI Assistant connects AI tools with a library of licensed assets, helping users find or generate visuals suitable for marketing, websites, and presentations. Here, you can create images that are safe for commercial use. Our AI Generator is trained only on licensed, ethically sourced content and follows clear rules to respect intellectual property, ensuring reliable results.","How does AI help graphic designers?":"How does AI help graphic designers?","AI helps speed up tasks such as searching for assets, generating visuals, and editing images. For example, with tools such as the DepositPhotos AI Assistant, designers can save time and streamline their creative workflow by:":"AI helps speed up tasks such as searching for assets, generating visuals, and editing images. For example, with tools such as the DepositPhotos AI Assistant, designers can save time and streamline their creative workflow by:","\u003Cstrong\u003EFast content discovery:\u003C/strong\u003E Instead of juggling keywords, users can search for the right assets with plain-language descriptions.":"\u003Cstrong\u003EFast content discovery:\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E Instead of juggling keywords, users can search for the right assets with plain-language descriptions.","\u003Cstrong\u003EUnique image generation:\u003C/strong\u003E A detailed prompt or a visual reference is enough to generate images perfectly aligned with any project.":"\u003Cstrong\u003EUnique image generation:\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E A detailed prompt or a visual reference is enough to generate images perfectly aligned with any project.","\u003Cstrong\u003EAccelerated revisions:\u003C/strong\u003E The AI assistant for designers helps adjust visuals on the fly without rebuilding designs from scratch.":"\u003Cstrong\u003EAccelerated revisions:\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E The AI assistant for designers helps adjust visuals on the fly without rebuilding designs from scratch.","As a result, designers can spend less time on repetitive tasks and more time focusing on creativity and strategy.":"As a result, designers can spend less time on repetitive tasks and more time focusing on creativity and strategy.","Can AI create branded marketing materials?":"Can AI create branded marketing materials?","Yes, AI can create branded marketing materials, especially when clear brand guidelines are in place. By combining the DepositPhotos AI Assistant with other graphic design tools like \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EVistaCreate\u003C/a\u003E, you can produce polished designs tailored to your brand identity.":"Yes, AI can create branded marketing materials, especially when clear brand guidelines are in place. By combining the DepositPhotos AI Assistant with other graphic design tools like \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EVistaCreate\u003C\u002Fa\u003E, you can produce polished designs tailored to your brand identity.","Use our creative AI assistant to find, generate, or edit assets that match your visual style. Then move to the VistaCreate design editor to integrate those visuals into ready-to-use marketing materials for social media, web, or print.":"Use our creative AI assistant to find, generate, or edit assets that match your visual style. Then move to the VistaCreate design editor to integrate those visuals into ready-to-use marketing materials for social media, web, or print.","Can agencies use AI-generated graphics for clients?":"Can agencies use AI-generated graphics for clients?","Agencies can use AI-generated graphics for client projects when they rely on AI design tools trained on commercially safe data, such as the DepositPhotos AI Image Generator. With it, you can be sure that the images don’t contain copyrighted logos, protected objects, or other elements that could lead to copyright infringement.":"Agencies can use AI-generated graphics for client projects when they rely on AI design tools trained on commercially safe data, such as the DepositPhotos AI Image Generator. With it, you can be sure that the images don’t contain copyrighted logos, protected objects, or other elements that could lead to copyright infringement.","In addition, generated images are provided under the \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EStandard License\u003C/a\u003E, allowing use in digital and print materials, including advertising and marketing campaigns.":"In addition, generated images are provided under the \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EStandard License\u003C\u002Fa\u003E, allowing use in digital and print materials, including advertising and marketing campaigns.","Does AI-generated content belong to me?":"Does AI-generated content belong to me?","Current copyright laws generally protect works created by human authors. However, images you generate using the DepositPhotos AI Assistant are licensed exclusively to you and will not be available to other users. Under the \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EStandard License\u003C/a\u003E, you also receive lifelong rights to use these images in both personal and commercial projects.":"Current copyright laws generally protect works created by human authors. However, images you generate using the DepositPhotos AI Assistant are licensed exclusively to you and will not be available to other users. Under the \u003Ca class=\"%s\" href=\"%s\" %s\u003EStandard License\u003C\u002Fa\u003E, you also receive lifelong rights to use these images in both personal and commercial projects.","What is the best AI assistant for designers?":"What is the best AI assistant for designers?","The best AI assistant for designers combines easy-to-use tools, an intuitive workflow, and high-quality results.":"The best AI assistant for designers combines easy-to-use tools, an intuitive workflow, and high-quality results.","The DepositPhotos AI Assistant simplifies the design process with:":"The DepositPhotos AI Assistant simplifies the design process with:","\u003Cstrong\u003EConversational experience:\u003C/strong\u003E Describe what you need in plain language and let the AI find, generate, or edit visuals for you.":"\u003Cstrong\u003EConversational experience:\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E Describe what you need in plain language and let the AI find, generate, or edit visuals for you.","\u003Cstrong\u003EFast and accurate output:\u003C/strong\u003E Quickly discover the right assets, refine images, or generate unique visuals from prompts.":"\u003Cstrong\u003EFast and accurate output:\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E Quickly discover the right assets, refine images, or generate unique visuals from prompts.","\u003Cstrong\u003EUser-friendly design:\u003C/strong\u003E Work in an intuitive interface that brings multiple creative features together in one place.":"\u003Cstrong\u003EUser-friendly design:\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E Work in an intuitive interface that brings multiple creative features together in one place.","Do I need design or AI experience to use it?":"Do I need design or AI experience to use it?","You don't need any design or AI experience to use the DepositPhotos AI Assistant. Whether you want to find assets, generate images, or edit them, you can do it using simple natural language prompts.":"You don't need any design or AI experience to use the DepositPhotos AI Assistant. Whether you want to find assets, generate images, or edit them, you can do it using simple natural language prompts.","To get started, simply describe what you need in the tool’s chat. For example: \u003Cem\u003E“Find a candid photo of a diverse Gen Z group laughing at a café, close-up shot.”\u003C/em\u003E Once the results appear, you can refine your request to improve the selection or customize a chosen image to match your vision.":"To get started, simply describe what you need in the tool’s chat. For example: \u003Cem\u003E“Find a candid photo of a diverse Gen Z group laughing at a café, close-up shot.”\u003C\u002Fem\u003E Once the results appear, you can refine your request to improve the selection or customize a chosen image to match your vision.","Are stock assets included?":"Are stock assets included?","With the AI Assistant, you can browse DepositPhotos’ library of %sM+ stock assets, including photos, videos, vectors, illustrations, and music files. Instead of guessing keywords, just describe the content and mood you’re looking for, and the assistant will quickly find the best matches. To download them, you’ll need an active plan.":"With the AI Assistant, you can browse DepositPhotos’ library of %sM+ stock assets, including photos, videos, vectors, illustrations, and music files. Instead of guessing keywords, just describe the content and mood you’re looking for, and the assistant will quickly find the best matches. To download them, you’ll need an active plan.","What editing tools are included?":"What editing tools are included?","Our AI design assistant includes tools such as:":"Our AI design assistant includes tools such as:","\u003Cstrong\u003EBackground Remover\u003C/strong\u003E that instantly erases the backdrop":"\u003Cstrong\u003EBackground Remover\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E that instantly erases the backdrop","\u003Cstrong\u003EImage Upscaler\u003C/strong\u003E that boosts resolution by up to 4x":"\u003Cstrong\u003EImage Upscaler\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E that boosts resolution by up to 4x","\u003Cstrong\u003EBackground Extender\u003C/strong\u003E that expands any scene in one click":"\u003Cstrong\u003EBackground Extender\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E that expands any scene in one click","\u003Cstrong\u003EObject Remover\u003C/strong\u003E that deletes unwanted elements from photos":"\u003Cstrong\u003EObject Remover\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E that deletes unwanted elements from photos","\u003Cstrong\u003EImage Resizer\u003C/strong\u003E that adjusts visuals to common aspect ratios":"\u003Cstrong\u003EImage Resizer\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E that adjusts visuals to common aspect ratios","How is the DepositPhotos AI assistant different from other tools?":"How is the DepositPhotos AI assistant different from other tools?","The DepositPhotos AI Assistant stands out among similar tools by offering a multifunctional experience that allows users to search licensed stock assets, generate commercially safe visuals, and edit images in a single workspace. This reduces the need to switch between platforms and supports a wide range of business and marketing use cases.":"The DepositPhotos AI Assistant stands out among similar tools by offering a multifunctional experience that allows users to search licensed stock assets, generate commercially safe visuals, and edit images in a single workspace. This reduces the need to switch between platforms and supports a wide range of business and marketing use cases.","Popular ideas":s,Discovery:"Discovery",Creation:"Creation","Image Editing":"Image Editing",Ideation:"Ideation","Search Images":"Search Images","Help me find the right stock images for my project. Ask a few quick questions to understand what I need, then suggest the best search keywords and visual styles.":"Help me find the right stock images for my project. Ask a few quick questions to understand what I need, then suggest the best search keywords and visual styles.","Search Videos":"Search Videos","Help me find the right stock video clips. Ask what the video will be used for, the mood, style, and format, then suggest the best search queries.":"Help me find the right stock video clips. Ask what the video will be used for, the mood, style, and format, then suggest the best search queries.","Search Audio":"Search Audio","Help me find suitable music or audio tracks. Ask about the purpose, mood, duration, and style, then recommend what to search for.":"Help me find suitable music or audio tracks. Ask about the purpose, mood, duration, and style, then recommend what to search for.","Find Similar":"Find Similar","I want to find visuals similar to what I already have. Ask me to upload or describe the reference, then help me discover close matches.":"I want to find visuals similar to what I already have. Ask me to upload or describe the reference, then help me discover close matches.","Generate Images":"Generate Images","Help me generate a new image with AI. Ask what I want to create, the subject, style, and use case, then write a strong generation prompt for me.":"Help me generate a new image with AI. Ask what I want to create, the subject, style, and use case, then write a strong generation prompt for me.","Generate Text":"Generate Text","Help me write marketing or creative text. Ask what it’s for, the tone, and the audience, then generate a polished draft.":"Help me write marketing or creative text. Ask what it’s for, the tone, and the audience, then generate a polished draft.","Remove Background":"Remove Background","Help me remove the background from an image. Ask me to upload the image and confirm what the final result should look like.":"Help me remove the background from an image. Ask me to upload the image and confirm what the final result should look like.","Resize Image":"Resize Image","Help me resize an image for my needs. Ask what platform or format it’s for (Instagram, ads, website, print), then suggest the best dimensions.":"Help me resize an image for my needs. Ask what platform or format it’s for (Instagram, ads, website, print), then suggest the best dimensions.","Help me improve the quality and resolution of an image. Ask me to upload it and confirm whether it’s for print, web, or large-scale use.":"Help me improve the quality and resolution of an image. Ask me to upload it and confirm whether it’s for print, web, or large-scale use.","Extend Background":"Extend Background","Help me extend the background of an image naturally. Ask me to upload the image and describe how much extra space I need and for what purpose.":"Help me extend the background of an image naturally. Ask me to upload the image and describe how much extra space I need and for what purpose.","Help me remove an unwanted object from an image. Ask me to upload the image and specify what should be removed, then guide the editing process.":"Help me remove an unwanted object from an image. Ask me to upload the image and specify what should be removed, then guide the editing process.","Get Ideas":"Get Ideas","Help me brainstorm creative visual ideas for my project. Ask what I’m working on, the goal, and the audience, then suggest concepts and directions.":"Help me brainstorm creative visual ideas for my project. Ask what I’m working on, the goal, and the audience, then suggest concepts and directions.","Discuss Campaign":"Discuss Campaign","Help me plan a marketing or creative campaign. Ask about the product, target audience, and channels, then propose visual themes and content ideas.":"Help me plan a marketing or creative campaign. Ask about the product, target audience, and channels, then propose visual themes and content ideas.","Upload Reference":"Upload Reference","I want to work from a reference image. Ask me to upload it and explain what I want to create or find based on it.":"I want to work from a reference image. Ask me to upload it and explain what I want to create or find based on it.","You have no generations available. Choose a plan to keep creating.":"You have no generations available. Choose a plan to keep creating.","Get a Plan":"Get a Plan","Authors you follow":"Authors you follow","Your favorite contributors are stored here. Enjoy quick access to their portfolios.":"Your favorite contributors are stored here. Enjoy quick access to their portfolios.","Like the author? Follow their account!":"Like the author? Follow their account!","Get quick access to their portfolio and don't miss out on important updates.":"Get quick access to their portfolio and don't miss out on important updates.","Never lose great content!":"Never lose great content!","Click the star icon on any file preview and add it to your Favorites folder. View, share, and download saved content anytime.":"Click the star icon on any file preview and add it to your Favorites folder. View, share, and download saved content anytime.","Try special feature":"Try special feature","Discover Favorites":"Discover Favorites","\u003Cstrong\u003ESave files for later\u003C/strong\u003E and organize them into folders. You'll find Favorites in the header.":"\u003Cstrong\u003ESave files for later\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E and organize them into folders. You'll find Favorites in the header.","Upgraded Favorites":"Upgraded Favorites","We've refreshed the icon and made the feature \u003Cstrong\u003Eeasier to spot\u003C/strong\u003E. The functionality stays the same—just more visible and convenient.":"We've refreshed the icon and made the feature \u003Cstrong\u003Eeasier to spot\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E. The functionality stays the same—just more visible and convenient.","Remove file backgrounds easily! Click the scissors icon, wait for AI to process, and download the background-free result to your device.":"Remove file backgrounds easily! Click the scissors icon, wait for AI to process, and download the background-free result to your device.","Remove Backgrounds in One Click":"Remove Backgrounds in One Click","Try & Save time":"Try & Save Time","Search Filters":"Search Filters","Find the files you need much faster with these search filters.":"Find the files you need much faster with these search filters.","Write a clear, descriptive prompt":"Write a clear, descriptive prompt","Describe your subject, location, and the action taking place. Add keywords specifying style, technique, mood, or aesthetic to generate your perfect image.":"Describe your subject, location, and the action taking place. Add keywords specifying style, technique, mood, or aesthetic to generate your perfect image.","Discover the full range of advanced AI-powered editing tools.":"Discover the full range of advanced AI-powered editing tools.","Transform your images in seconds. Instantly remove or extend backgrounds, erase objects, enhance quality, modify people, or reimagine your photo—all with one click.":"Transform your images in seconds. Instantly remove or extend backgrounds, erase objects, enhance quality, modify people, or reimagine your photo—all with one click.","Meet your new AI Assistant—here to help you search, create, and edit, all in one place.":"Meet your new AI Assistant—here to help you search, create, and edit, all in one place.","Visual Search":"Visual Search","Get better results with a reference image! Just upload a file here.":"Get better results with a reference image! \u003Cbr\u003EJust upload a file here.","%s free extra image downloads per month have been successfully added. You get extra images as long as your plan is active.":"%s free extra image downloads per month have been successfully added. You get extra images as long as your plan is active.","Your plan’s price is protected for %s months.":"Your plan’s price is protected for %s months.","+%s images /month":"+%s images \u002Fmonth","A %s discount on your current plan's future renewals has been successfully activated.":"A %s discount on your current plan's future renewals has been successfully activated.","By keeping auto-renewal \u003Cb\u003Eturned ON\u003C/b\u003E, your downloads will never expire. Unused downloads will be transferred to the next month.":"By keeping auto-renewal \u003Cb\u003Eturned ON\u003C\u002Fb\u003E, your downloads will never expire. Unused downloads will be transferred to the next month.","Image Plans":"Image Plans","Video Plans":"Video Plans","Audio Plans":"Audio Plans","Create \u003Cspan class=\"%s\"\u003E\"%s\"\u003C/span\u003E images with \u003Cspan class=\"%s\"\u003EAI Image Generator\u003C/span\u003E":"Create \u003Cspan class=\"%s\"\u003E\"%s\"\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E images with \u003Cspan class=\"%s\"\u003EAI Image Generator\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E","Describe the image you want to create":"Describe the image you want to create","Enter a theme you want to explore":"Enter a theme you want to explore","Plans & Balance":"Plans & Balance",Balance:"Balance","Active Plans":"Active Plans","Try Starter Pack":"Try Starter Pack","%s images for %s":"%s images for %s","%s pic downloads & AI generation":"%s pic downloads & AI generation","%s days free!":"%s days free!","To save this image, create an account":"To save this image, create an account","To save this video, create an account":"To save this video, create an account","To save this audio, create an account":"To save this audio, create an account","Saved to":"Saved to",Manage:"Manage",Cashback:"Cashback","Your Favorites":"Your Favorites","Sign In":h,"Register an Account":a,"Current page %s":"Current page %s","Your Manager":"Your Manager","Not sure what to search?":"Not sure what to search?","Let the assistant guide your search and turn your ideas into images.":"Let the Assistant guide your search and turn your ideas into images.","Voice dictation":"Voice dictation","Close banner":"Close banner","Try our new Search by Image!":"Try our new Search by Image.",Generate:"Generate","Open your account menu":"Open your account menu","Get Help":"Get help","Point of view":"Point of View","Season, Time of day":"Season, Time of Day","Size of image":"Image Size",Mood:"Moods",Genre:"Genres","Sound Effects":c,Type:"Type",Contributor:bb,"Date Added":"Date Added","Origin and Location":"Origin & Location","AI Content":"AI Content","Vector type":"Vector type",Orientation:"Orientation","Illustration type":"Illustration Type",Technique:"Technique","Image upload error":"Image upload error","Necessary cookies":"Necessary cookies","These cookies are always active to ensure the website functions properly. They keep you securely logged in, remember your privacy settings, and enable smooth navigation. They do not collect any information for marketing or advertising purposes.":"These cookies are always active to ensure the website functions properly. They keep you securely logged in, remember your privacy settings, and enable smooth navigation. They do not collect any information for marketing or advertising purposes.","Functional cookies":"Functional cookies","We use these cookies to understand how you use our website, for example, which pages are popular or how long you stay. This data is collected anonymously and helps us improve site performance and tailor content to your needs.":"We use these cookies to understand how you use our website, for example, which pages are popular or how long you stay. This data is collected anonymously and helps us improve site performance and tailor content to your needs.","Advertising cookies":"Advertising cookies","These cookies help us show you ads that are more relevant to your interests and measure how well our campaigns perform. We may share limited, non-personal data with Google to improve ad delivery across their services. This information is handled securely and only shared with your explicit consent.":"These cookies help us show you ads that are more relevant to your interests and measure how well our campaigns perform. We may share limited, non-personal data with Google to improve ad delivery across their services. This information is handled securely and only shared with your explicit consent.","Personalization cookies":"Personalization cookies","These cookies personalize your experience by adjusting the ads you see based on your activity and interests. They are optional. If disabled, you'll still see ads, but they won't be tailored to you.":"These cookies personalize your experience by adjusting the ads you see based on your activity and interests. They are optional. If disabled, you'll still see ads, but they won't be tailored to you.","Folder Permissions":"Folder Permissions","\"%s\" folder is available to you in a \"Read-only\" format. Please contact the owner of the folder for permission to edit.":"\"%s\" folder is available to you in a \"Read-only\" format. Please contact the owner of the folder for permission to edit.","Added to":"Added to","\u003Cspan class=\"%s\"\u003ECreate your Account\u003C/span\u003E to add this video to your Favorites":"\u003Cspan class=\"%s\"\u003ECreate your account\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E to add this video to your Favorites","\u003Cspan class=\"%s\"\u003ECreate your Account\u003C/span\u003E to add this image to your Favorites":"\u003Cspan class=\"%s\"\u003ECreate your account\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E to add this image to your Favorites","Select a Folder":"Select a Folder","Please select a folder in your Favorites to add the selected file to.":"Please select a folder in your Favorites to add the selected file to.","The \"%s\" folder is read-only. To save this file, please choose another folder or ask the folder owner for edit permissions.":"The \"%s\" folder is read-only. To save this file, please choose another folder or ask the folder owner for edit permissions.","Too many files selected":"Too many files selected","You've selected %s files, but it's only possible to license up to %s at a time. Please contact our \u003Ca href=\"%s\" class=\"%s\"\u003ECustomer Support team\u003C/a\u003E to help resolve this issue.":"You've selected %s files, but it's only possible to license up to %s at a time. Please contact our \u003Ca href=\"%s\" class=\"%s\"\u003ECustomer Support team\u003C\u002Fa\u003E to help resolve this issue.","Okay, thanks!":"Okay, thanks!","The file you have selected is from our Focused Collection. To license it, please contact your Depositphotos manager.":"The file you have selected is from our Focused Collection. To license it, please contact your DepositPhotos manager.","You've successfully purchased the license for the file.":"You've successfully purchased the license for the file.","Licensing in Progress":"Licensing in Progress","Please wait while we prepare your files. A link to download a ZIP folder will be sent to \u003Cspan class=\"%s\"\u003E%s\u003C/span\u003E.":"Please wait while we prepare your files. A link to download a ZIP folder will be sent to \u003Cspan class=\"%s\"\u003E%s\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E.","Please wait while we process the licensing of your files.":"Please wait while we process the licensing of your files.","Files per Page":bc,"Select folder to save Favorites":bd,"Hide downloaded":be,"File Type Icon":bf,"Show Maximum File Size":bg,"Show Length for Videos":bh,"Open File Links in a New Window":bi,"Adult Filter (Safe Search)":bj,"Show Related Searches":bk,"Search settings":bl,Personal:aX,Enterprise:"Enterprise","Contribute Program":"Contributor Program",Downloads:I,"Log Out":"Log Out","API Keys":"API Keys","Free Collection":"Free Collection","API Manual":"API Manual","API Plans & Prices":"API Plans & Prices","%s must contain at least %s characters.":bm,"Earned Money":"Earned Money","Cashback Balance":"Cashback Balance","Account Balance":"Account Balance",Saved:"Saved","Clip Keywords":"Clip Keywords","Stock Illustration Keywords":"Stock Illustration Keywords","Stock Vector Keywords":